Ukwanda okusheshayo kokugcwala kwesifo se-coronavirus (COVID-19) e-European Union/European Economic Area nase-United Kingdom, kusukela ngomhlaka 1 kuJanuwari kuya ku-15 Mashi 2020
Ukubhebhetheka okuhlanganisiwe kwezigameko zesifo se-coronavirus (i-COVID-19) kubonisa ukuthambekela okufanayo emazweni ase-European Union/European Economic Area kanye nase-United Kingdom okuqinisekisa ukuthi, nakuba sesesigabeni esihlukile kuye ngezwe, ubhadane lwe-COVID-19 luqhubeka ngokushesha kuwo wonke amazwe.
Ngokusekelwe kokuhlangenwe nakho okuvela e-Italy, amazwe, izibhedlela kanye namayunithi okunakekela abagulayo kufanele akhulise ukulungela kwawo ukwanda kweziguli ezine-COVID-19 ezizodinga ukunakekelwa kwezempilo, ikakhulukazi ukunakekelwa okugcwele.
Ngo-December 31, 2019, kwabikwa inqwaba yamacala omdlavuza wamaphaphu anesifo esingaziwa eWuhan, esifundazweni saseHubei, eChina.
Ngo-January 9, 2020, iChina Center for Disease Control and Prevention yabika ukuthi i-agent ebangela lesi sifo iyinoveli coronavirus manje ebizwa ngokuthi i-severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kusukela lapho, lesi sifo esibangelwa ukutheleleka yi-SARS-CoV-2 sibizwa ngokuthi isifo se-coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ubufakazi obukhona kuze kube manje bubonisa ukuthi cishe abantu abangama-80% abane-COVID-19 banesifo esincane, okungukuthi, ukutheleleka kwemigudu yokuphefumula nge-pneumonia noma ngaphandle kwayo, futhi iningi labo liyapholisa.
Ezimweni ezingaba ngu-14% i-COVID-19 iba isifo esibi kakhulu esidinga ukulaliswa esibhedlela kanti ezisele ezingu-6% zibhekana nesifo esibucayi esidinga ukunakekelwa okujulile.
Ukufa kweziguli ezilaliswe esibhedlela ngenxa ye-COVID-19 cishe kungamaphesenti angu-4.
Kulolu cwaningo, sihlola ukuthambekela kokugcwala kwe-COVID-19 ezweni ngalinye le-European Union/European Economic Area (EU/EEA) nase-United Kingdom (UK) bese siyakuqhathanisa neSifundazwe saseHubei, eChina.
Siphinde siqhathanise inani lamanje lamacala e-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK nelase-Italy phakathi kuka-31 Januwari no-15 Mashi 2020.
Izimo ze-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK
Ngemva kweChina, i-COVID-19 yaqhubeka nokusabalala ngokomhlaba futhi izinga lobhadane lwe-COVID-19 emhlabeni wonke okwamanje lilandela lelo laleli zwe.
Ngo-11 Mashi 2020, uMqondisi-Jikelele we-World Health Organization (WHO) wamemezela i-COVID-19 njengobhadane.
Kumagazini ka-March 5 we-Eurosurveillance 2020, uSpiteri et al. babika ngamacala okuqala e-Europe aqinisekisiwe e-COVID-19 ngokusho kwencazelo yecala le-WHO.
E-EU/EEA, amacala amathathu okuqala aqinisekisiwe abikwa yiFrance ngo-January 24, 2020 kubantu ababuya eWuhan, esifundazweni saseHubei, eChina.
NgoMashi 15, 2020, amacala e-COVID-19 ayetholakala kuwo wonke amazwe angu-30 e-EU/EEA nase-United Kingdom (UK), lapho phakathi kuka-December 31, 2019 kanye nalolo suku, kubikwa khona amacala angu-39,768 nokufa okungu-1,727 kanti e-Italy kuphela, kwavela amacala angu-17,750 nokufa okungu-1,441.
Ukuthola inani eliqoqiwe kanye nokugcwala okuqoqiwe kwezigameko ze-COVID-19
E-European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control (ECDC), inani lamacala abikwe nge-COVID-19 ezweni ngalinye emhlabeni wonke, elitholakala emithonjeni esemthethweni kuphela njenge-Ministry of Health, iziphathimandla zezempilo zikazwelonke nezesifunda kanye ne-WHO, libuyekezwa nsuku zonke ngo-8:00 ekuseni.
Le mininingwane isetshenziselwe ukuhlola ukuthambekela kwe-COVID-19 e-EU/EEA nase-UK, nokuyiqhathanisa ne-Italy.
Njengomlinganisi wokugcwala kwamacala asebenzayo e-COVID-19, sibale inani elihlanganisiwe lezinsuku eziyi-14 lamacala e-COVID-19, ngaleyo ndlela sicabangela inkambo yemvelo ye-COVID-19, ezweni ngalinye le-EU/EEA nase-UK, phakathi nenkathi ka-1 Januwari 15 Mashi 2020.
Siphinde saveza inani eliqoqiwe lamacala abikiwe ezweni ngalinye ngomhlaka-15 Mashi 2020 ngo-8:00 ekuseni uma kuqhathaniswa nelase-Italy ngesikhathi sika-31 Januwari-15 Mashi 2020.
Izimo ze-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK
Izimo ezenzeka ezinsukwini ezingu-14 ezihlanganisiwe zezigameko ze-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK ngokuvamile zilandela ezaseSifundazweni saseHubei (eChina) (Umdwebo 1).
E-EU/EEA nase-UK, inani eliqoqiwe le-COVID-19 laqala ukwanda cishe ngo-21 February, lase lenyuka kakhulu cishe ngo-28 February 2020 (Izinto ezengeziwe).
Lokhu kwakubangelwa kakhulu ukwanda okusheshayo kwenani lamacala abikiwe e-Italy, kodwa wonke amanye amazwe e-EU/EEA kanye ne-UK babonisa ukuthambekela okufanayo kokwanda kokugcwala kwe-COVID-19 (Izinto ezengeziwe).
Umdwebo 2 ubonisa inani eliqoqiwe lamacala e-COVID-19, emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK uma kuqhathaniswa nelase-Italy ngesikhathi sika-31 Januwari- 15 Mashi 2020.
Iphinde iqokomise ukuthi ngo-15 March ngo-8:00 ekuseni, amanye amazwe angu-15 e-EU/EEA ne-UK ayesevele ebike inani eliphelele lamacala elilingana nelase-Italy emasontweni amathathu nje ngaphambili noma ngaphansi.
Imiphumela yethu ibonisa ukuthi inani lamacala abikiwe e-COVID-19 liyanda ngokushesha e-EU/EEA nase-UK.
Izimo ezibonwayo zokubhebhetheka kwe-COVID-19 zikhombisa ukuthi ubhadane luqhubeka ngesivinini esiqhathaniswayo kuwo wonke amazwe.
Lokhu kwenzeka yize amazwe esezigabeni ezihlukene, ukuhlukahluka kwezimpendulo zezempilo yomphakathi kazwelonke, kanye nezincazelo zamaphuzu ahlukene emazweni kanye nezinqubo ezahlukene zokukhetha iziguli okumele zihlolwe ukuze kuqinisekiswe i-COVID-19, kubandakanya nokuhlolwa kokufika.
Ekuqaleni kuka-March 2020, odokotela ezifundeni ezithintekile e-Italy bachaza isimo lapho cishe abangu-10% beziguli ezine-COVID-19 bedinga ukunakekelwa okujulile futhi imithombo yabezindaba yabika ukuthi izibhedlela namayunithi okunakekelwa okujulile kulezi zifunda asevele afinyelele umthamo wawo ophezulu.
Okwamanje, imininingwane yokwamukelwa kweziguli ze-COVID-19 esibhedlela kanye/noma emagunjini okunakekela abagula kakhulu itholakala ezingeni le-EU/EEA kuphela kuma-6% kanye no-1% wamacala, ngokulandelana (imininingwane ayiboniswa).
Nokho, kufanele ziqoqwe ngendlela ehlelekile ukuze kuhlanganiswe nemininingwane yamanje yokuqapha egxile enanini lamacala abikiwe nenani labafile.
Ucwaningo olwenziwa ngo-201011 lwabonisa ukwehluka okukhulu kokutholakala kwemibhede yokunakekela okunzulu kanye nemibhede yokunakekela okuphakathi eYurophu, kusukela ku-29,2 eJalimane kuya ku-4,2 emibhedeni kubantu abangu-100 000 ePortugal.
Lokhu kusho ukuthi amazwe angase abe nezinsiza eziningi noma ezimbalwa kune-Italy (izimoto ezingu-12,5 zokunakekelwa okujulile nezomnyango ophakathi nendawo kubantu abangu-100 000 ngo-2010).
Izimo zokumodela ezihlobene nokugcwala kwamandla okunakekelwa kwezempilo, nezibalo zezwe ngalinye le-EU/EEA ne-UK zokugcwala kwamacala e-COVID-19 alaliswe esibhedlela ahambisana nengozi engamaphesenti angaphezu kwangu-90 yokweqa umthamo wemibhede yokunakekelwa okujulile, zinikezwe ekubuyekezweni kwesithupha kokuhlolwa kwengozi okusheshayo kwe-ECDC nge-COVID-19.
Njengoba kuze kube manje amacala aye agxunyekwe ezifundeni ezithile emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK, futhi izibhedlela namayunithi okunakekela abagulayo ngokuvamile asebenza kubantu abazinikezele esifundeni, ulwazi ngamacala nemibhede yokunakekela abagulayo kufanele kutholakale ezingeni le-Nomenclature of territorial units for statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Okuhlangenwe nakho kwase-Italy nezimo zamanje kwamanye amazwe kubonisa ukuthi ubhadane lwe-COVID-19 luqhubeka ngokushesha e-EU/EEA nase-UK.
Amazwe, izibhedlela kanye namayunithi okunakekela abagulayo kufanele azilungiselele isimo sokudluliselwa komphakathi okuqhubekayo kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kanye nokwanda kwenani leziguli ezine-COVID-19 ezidinga ukunakekelwa kwezempilo, futhi ikakhulukazi ukunakekelwa okugcwele, njengalokhu okwenzeka ezifundeni ezithintekile e-Italy.
Njengoba kukhonjisiwe ekuhlolweni kwamuva kwezingozi okusheshayo kwe-ECDC, indlela esheshayo, esebenzayo nebanzi ibalulekile ukuze kubambezele ukusabalala kwe-SARS-COV-2, ngokushintsha indlela yokuvimbela ibe indlela yokunciphisa, njengoba ukwanda okusheshayo okulindelekile kwenani lamacala kungase kungabunikezi abathathi bezinqumo nezibhedlela isikhathi esanele sokuqonda, ukwamukela nokulungisa ukusabela kwabo ngokufanele uma kungasetshenziswa kusenesikhathi.
Ukuhlolwa kwengozi okusheshayo kuhlanganisa nezinyathelo zezempilo zomphakathi zokunciphisa umthelela walolu bhubhane.
Kunesikhathi esifushane lapho amazwe enethuba lokwandisa imizamo yawo yokulawula ukuze anciphise ukusabalala kwe-SARS-CoV-2 futhi anciphise ingcindezi ekunakekelweni kwezempilo.
Uma lokhu kungenzeki, kungenzeka ukuthi izinhlelo zokunakekelwa kwezempilo kwamanye amazwe e-EU/EEA zizobhekana nokwanda kweziguli ezidinga ukunakekelwa okujulile ezinsukwini noma emasontweni ezayo.
Ukuqubuka kwesifo i-Coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19), okubangelwa i-severe acute respiratory syndrome (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kuze kube manje sekubulale abantu abangaphezu kuka-3 000 futhi kwashaya abangaphezu kuka-80,000 eChina nakwezinye izindawo emhlabeni, okuholele enhlekeleleni kubantu.
Ngokufana negciwane layo elifana nalo, i-SARS-CoV, eyabangela i-SARS ezinkulungwaneni zabantu ngo-2003, i-SARS-CoV-2 nayo ingadluliselwa emibuthweni futhi ibangele izimpawu ezifanayo ngomshini ofanayo.
Nokho, i-COVID-19 inezinga eliphansi lokuqina nokufa kune-SARS kodwa iyathathelana kakhulu futhi ithinta abantu asebekhulile kakhulu kunentsha futhi ithinta amadoda amaningi kunabesifazane.
Ngenxa yokwanda okusheshayo kwezincwadi ezikhuluma ngalesi sifo esisha, lesi sihloko sizama ukunikeza ukubuyekeza okufika ngesikhathi futhi okuphelele kwalesi sihloko esicwaninga ngokushesha.
Sizohlola izinto eziyisisekelo eziphathelene nesifo esiwumshayabhuqe, isifo esibangela ukuqubuka kwezifo, isifo esibangelwa amagciwane, ukuxilongwa, ukwelashwa, ukuhlolwa kwesimo esibi, nokuvinjelwa kwalesi sifo.
Nakuba kusenezicelo eziningi ezisafuna izimpendulo, sinethemba lokuthi lokhu kubuyekezwa kuyosiza ekuqondeni nasekuqothulweni kwalesi sifo esisongelayo.
UMkhosi Wentwasahlobo ngoJanuwari 25, 2020 uye waba yisikhumbuzo esingenakuqhathaniswa nesingasoze salibaleka kubo bonke abantu baseChina abacelwe ukuba bahlale emakhaya kulo lonke leli holide nasemasontweni amaningi ngemva kwalokho ngenxa yokuqubuka kwesifo esisha esibangelwa amagciwane.
Leli gciwane lifana kakhulu ne-coronavirus (CoV) eyabangela ukuqubuka kwe-severe acute respiratory syndrome (SARS) ngo-2003; ngakho-ke, yaqanjwa ngokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 yi-World Health Organization (WHO) ngoFebhuwari 11, 2020, futhi isifo esihambisanayo sabizwa ngokuthi i-CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Lolu bhubhane lwaqala eWuhan, eChina, futhi lwasakazeka ngokushesha kulo lonke izwe futhi lwafinyelela kwamanye angaba ngu-50 emhlabeni wonke.
Kusukela ngoMashi 2, 2020, leli gciwane seliholele emacaleni angaphezu kuka-80,000 aqinisekisiwe e-COVID-19, neziguli ezingaphezu kuka-40,000 ezikhishwe esibhedlela neziguli ezingaphezu kuka-3,000 ezife.
I-WHO ixwayisa ngokuthi i-COVID-19 iyisitha somphakathi esingu-1 futhi kungenzeka ukuthi inamandla ngaphezu kobuphekula.
Ngokwe-PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), esikhathini esingaphansi kwezinyanga ezimbili, sekushicilelwe amaphepha angaphezu kuka-200 nge-COVID-19 kuhlanganise ne-virology yayo, i-epidemiology, i-etiology, ukuxilongwa, nokwelashwa kusukela embikweni wokuqala ngoJanuwari 7, 2020 owanquma ukulandelana kwegciwane elihlukaniswe ezigulini eziningi.
Lesi sibuyekezo sizama ukufingqa inqubekela phambili yocwaningo kule ndawo entsha futhi eshintsha ngokushesha.
Noma nini lapho kungenzeka, sizozama ukuqhathanisa i-COVID-19 ne-SARS kanye nesinye isifo esibangelwa i-COV, i-Middle East respiratory syndrome (i-MERS, ukuqubuka ngo-2012).
Sizophinde sixoxe ngalokho esikufundile kuze kube manje ngokuphathelene nokuvimbela nokubona ukuthi lesi sifo singenzeka kanjani kanye neminye imibuzo esisele kodwa ephuthumayo.
Ama-CoV aye abhekwa njengama-pathogen angenabungozi kubantu, ikakhulukazi abangela cishe amaphesenti angu-15 amakhaza avamile 4.
Nokho, kule nkulungwane, sihlangane nama-CoV abantu anezifo eziyingozi kakhulu kabili, okungukuthi, i-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV, eyabangela ukuqubuka eChina ngo-2003 naseSaudi Arabia ngo-2012, ngokulandelana, futhi ngokushesha yasakazekela kwamanye amazwe amaningi ngokugula okukhulu nokufa.
Ngakho-ke, i-COVID-19 yamanje ingumqedazwe wesithathu we-Cov emlandweni wabantu.
Njengoba kuboniswe esithombeni 1,1, kwaqala ukubikwa izifo zesifo samaphaphu ezazingaziwa ukuthi zavela kuphi eWuhan ngoDisemba 31, 2019 eChina National Health Commission.
Ezinsukwini eziyisikhombisa kamuva kwaqhamuka uhlu lwe-CoV.
NgoJanuwari 15, 2020 kwabikwa icala lokuqala elibulalayo eWuhan.
Phakathi naleso sikhathi, lesi sifo sasakazekela ngokushesha emadolobheni, ezifundazweni, nasemazweni angomakhelwane.
Ngo-January 20, kwabikwa ukutheleleka kwabanikezeli bezokwelapha, okusikisela ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi umuntu adluliselwe komunye umuntu.
Ngo-January 23, idolobha laseWuhan lavalwa futhi zonke izinto zokuhamba zomphakathi zavalwa.
Ngo-January 24 ucwaningo lokuqala lwezokwelapha ngalesi sifo lwabika ukuthi, ezigulini ezingu-41 ezinezimo eziqinisekisiwe, ezingu-21 kuphela ezazithintana ngqo nemakethe yezilwane zasolwandle eWuhan okwakubhekwa njengendawo yokuqala ukutheleleka okuvela emthonjeni wesilwane ongaziwa.
Ngo-January 30, i-WHO yamemezela lesi sifo njengesiphuthumayo emhlabeni wonke.
