La ma-cytokine enza amangqamuzana omzimba avimbelayo ukuba akhiphe inani elikhulu lama-radicals akhululekile angimbangela eyinhloko ye-ARDS nokuhluleka kwamalungu amaningi.
Ukumelana nemithi yokugoma kuyadingeka ekwelapheni iziphepho ze- cytokine, ikakhulukazi ezigulini ezinzima.
Ama-corticosteroids ne-tocilizumab, okuyi-anti-IL6 monoclonal antibody, aye asetshenziselwa ukwelapha isiyaluyalu se-cytokine.
Ezinye izindlela zokwelapha zokunqanda ukungasebenzi kahle komzimba ezibhekene nesiphepho samakhemikhali i- cytokine zihlanganisa ukulawula ukusabela komzimba okuqondiswa amangqamuzana e- T; ukuvimbela i- IFN-Œ≥, i- IL-1, ne- TNF; ukuvimbela i- JAK; i- blinatumomab; ukuvimbela ukusakaza amasignali kwama- cytokine 4; kanye nama- HDAC inhibitors.
Ama-steroid, njengezinto ezikhuthaza ukuzivikela komzimba, asetshenziswa kabanzi ekwelapheni i-SARS ukuze kuncishiswe ukulimala okubangelwa ukuvuvukala.
Nokho, ama-steroid ngamanani aphakeme awazange abe nenzuzo ekulimaleni okukhulu kwamaphaphu ezigulini ze-SARS ne-COVID-19.
Kunalokho, zingase zibangele imiphumela emibi kakhulu, ikakhulukazi i-osteonecrosis ye-avascular, ethinta kakhulu isimo.
Noma kunjalo, kunconywa ukuba kusetshenziswe ngokuqapha ama-corticosteroids amafushane ngamanani aphansi kuya kwaphakathi ezigulini eziphethwe yi-COVID-19 ezigula kakhulu.
Ngesikhathi kulotshwa le ncwadi, awukho umuthi wokwelapha owenziwe waba nethonya eliphumelelayo.
Nokho, ukufakwa kwe-remdesivir, okuyi-nucleotide analog, emthanjeni kuye kwabonakala kuyasebenza esigulini saseMelika esine-COVID-19.
I-Remdesivir iwumuthi omusha olwa namagciwane owakhiwa iGilead ekuqaleni ukuze kulashwe izifo ezibangelwa amagciwane e-Ebola neMarlburg.
Kamuva, i-remdesivir yabonisa nokuthi kungenzeka ukuthi ivimbela amanye amagciwane e-RNA anesitayela esisodwa kuhlanganise namagciwane e-MERS ne-SARS.
Ngokusekelwe kulokhu, iGilead inikeze i-compound eChina ukuze kwenziwe izivivinyo ezimbili kubantu abatheleleke nge-SARS-CoV-2, futhi imiphumela ilindelwe kakhulu.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, i- baricitinb, i- interferon- Œ±, i- lopinavir/ ritonavir, ne- ribavirin kuye kwasikiselwa njengendlela yokwelapha engaba khona ezigulini ezinezimpawu ezibucayi zokuphefumula.
Ukuhlanza, isicanucanu, ukuhlanza, ukulimala kwesibindi, neminye imiphumela emibi kungenzeka ngemva kokwelashwa okuhlangene ne- lopinavir/ ritonavir.
Ukuhlangana kwalezi zindlela zokwelapha nezinye izidakamizwa ezisetshenziswa ezigulini kufanele kuqaphelwe ngokucophelela.
I-plasma yeziguli eziphulukisiwe nokukhiqizwa kwama-antibody
Umlando omude wokuqoqwa kwegazi ezigulini ezasinda esifweni esithathelwanayo ukuze kulashwe ezinye iziguli ezinesifo esifanayo noma ukuvikela abantu abaphilile ukuba bangabambeki yilesi sifo.
Ngempela, iziguli eziye zaphola ngokuvamile zinamazinga aphakeme kakhulu emagciwane alwa nalesi sifo egazini lazo.
Ama-antibody ayi-immunoglobulin (Ig) ekhiqizwa ama-lymphocyte ase-B ukuze alwe namagciwane nezinye izinto eziyimpicabadala futhi ayazazi izinhlayiya eziyingqayizivele kuma-pathogen futhi azivimbe ngokuqondile.
Ngokusekelwe kulokhu, i-plasma yaqoqwa egazini leqembu leziguli ezaphola ku-COVID-19 futhi yanikezwa iziguli ezingu-10 ezigula kakhulu.
Izimpawu zabo zathuthuka emahoreni angu-24, zalandelelwa ukunciphisa ukuvuvukala nokushaja kwegciwane nokuthuthuka kokugcwala komoya-mpilo egazini.
Nokho, kudingeka ukuqinisekiswa nokucaciswa ukuze kuphakanyiswe indlela yokusetshenziswa ngezinga elikhulu ngaphambi kokuba kusungulwe izindlela zokwelapha ezithile.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ngenxa yemiphumela yokwelapha, kufanele kucatshangelwe ngokucophelela ezinye zezinto ezingazuzisi ezihlobene ne-plasma.
Ngokwesibonelo, ama - antibody angahle avuse ukusabela komzimba okuvimbela izifo ngokweqile futhi abangele i - cytokine release syndrome, okungase kube ubuthi obungase busongele ukuphila.
Ngokuvamile izinga lama - antibody egazini liphansi, futhi isidingo se - plasma sikhulu ekwelapheni iziguli ezigula kakhulu.
Kunzima ukuthuthukisa nokukhiqiza ama - antibody athile ngokushesha ngokwanele ukuze kulwelwe ubhadane lomhlaba wonke.
Ngakho-ke, kubaluleke kakhulu futhi kuyasebenza ukuhlukanisa amangqamuzana e-B ezigulini eziye zaphola futhi ubone amakhodi ezifuzo abhala ama-antibody asebenzayo noma ukuhlola ama-antibody asebenzayo emelana namaprotheni abalulekile egciwane.
Ngale ndlela, singakwazi ukukhulisa ukukhiqizwa kwama-antibody kalula.
I-TCM isetshenziselwa ukwelapha izifo ezihlukahlukene eChina izinkulungwane zeminyaka.
Nokho, imiphumela yayo incike kakhulu ekuhlanganisweni kwezakhi eziningi ezisefomula elihlukahluka kuye ngokuthi isifo sihlolwe kanjani ngokwemibono ye-TCM.
Iningi lezakhi ezisebenzayo lisaziwa noma alicaci ngoba kunzima ukukhipha nokuqinisekisa lezozakhi noma inhlanganisela yazo efanele.
Njengamanje, ngenxa yokuntuleka kokwelashwa okusebenzayo nokungokuthile kwe-COVID-19, i-TCM isibe enye yezindlela ezinkulu zokwelashwa ezigulini ezinezimpawu ezincane kuya kwezingaphakathi noma kulabo asebeke balulama ezigabeni ezinzima.
Ngokwesibonelo, kwatholakala ukuthi ama-capsule ka-Shu Feng Jie Du nama-capsule ka-Lian Hua Qing Wen ayasebenza ekwelapheni i-COVID-19.
Izinga eliphezulu lokwelashwa kweziguli ze-COVID-19 labonwa ezifundazweni eziningana eChina ezasebenzisa i-TCM ezigulini ezingu-87%, kuhlanganise neGansu (63.7%), i-Ningxia (50%), neHunan (50%), kuyilapho isifundazwe saseHubei, esasebenzisa i-TCM cishe kuphela ezigulini ezingu-30% zeziguli zayo ze-COVID-19, sasinezinga eliphansi kakhulu lokwelashwa (13%).
Nokho, lokhu kuqhathanisa akuyona into elula ngoba ezinye izici eziningi ezinjengesibalo nesisindo seziguli kufanele zifakwe ekuhloleni.
NgoFebhuwari 18, 2020, uBoli Zhang nozakwabo bashicilela ucwaningo lokuqhathanisa ukwelashwa kwezokwelapha zaseNtshonalanga (WM) kuphela nokwelashwa okuhlangene kwe-WM ne-TCM.
Bathola ukuthi isikhathi esidingekayo sokululama kokushisa komzimba, ukunyamalala kwezimpawu, nokulaliswa esibhedlela sasimfushane kakhulu eqenjini le-WM + TCM kunaseqenjini le-WM kuphela.
Okuhlaba umxhwele kakhulu ukuthi izinga lokonakala kwezifo (kusukela kokulula kuya kokunzima) laliphansi kakhulu eqenjini le-WM + TCM kunelaseqenjini le-WM kuphela (7,4% uma kuqhathaniswa no-46,2%) futhi ukufa kwakuncane eqenjini le-WM + TCM kunelaseqenjini le-WM kuphela (8,8% uma kuqhathaniswa no-39%).
Noma kunjalo, ukusebenza kahle nokuphepha kwe-TCM kusalindele ukuhlolwa okuningiliziwe ngezinga elikhulu nasezikhungweni eziningi.
Kungaba mnandi futhi ukuchaza indlela esebenza ngayo nokucacisa izingxenye ezisebenzayo zokwelashwa kwe-TCM noma ukuhlanganiswa kwazo uma kungenzeka.
Iziguli ezisolwa noma eziqinisekisiwe nge-COVID-19 zivame ukubhekana nokwesaba okukhulu kwalesi sifo esithelelanayo ngisho nesingabulalayo, futhi abantu abavalelwe bodwa nabo babhekana nesithukuthezi, isizungu nentukuthelo.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, izimpawu zokutheleleka ezifana nomkhuhlane, i-hypoxia, nokukhwehlela kanye nemiphumela emibi yokwelashwa njengokungalali okubangelwa ama-corticosteroid kungaholela ekukhathazekeni okukhulu nasekucindezelekeni kwengqondo.
Esigabeni sokuqala sokuqubuka kwe-SARS, kwabikwa izifo eziningi zengqondo ezihlanganisa ukucindezeleka okuqhubekayo, ukukhathazeka, ukuhlaselwa ukwesaba, ukuvusa ingqondo, izimpawu zengqondo, ukuhlanekezela, ngisho nokuzibulala.
Ukuxilongwa okuyimpoqo nokuhlukaniswa, njengengxenye yezimpendulo zezempilo yomphakathi ekuqubukeni kwe-COVID-19, kungenza abantu bakhathazeke futhi babe necala ngemiphumela yokutheleleka, ukuhlukaniswa, kanye nokucwaswa emindenini yabo nakubangane.
Ngakho-ke, ukunakekelwa kwengqondo kufanele kunikezwe iziguli ze-COVID-19, abantu abasolwayo, nabantu abasondelene nabo kanye nomphakathi jikelele oswele.
Ukusekelwa ngokwengqondo kufanele kufake phakathi ukusungulwa kwamaqembu ezempilo yengqondo ahlukahlukene, ukuxhumana okucacile okunezibuyekezo ezijwayelekile nezinembile mayelana nokuqubuka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 nezinhlelo zokwelashwa nokusetshenziswa kwamadivayisi nezinhlelo zokusebenza zobuchwepheshe ukuze kugwenywe ukuxhumana eduze komunye nomunye.
Imishanguzo ephumelelayo ibalulekile ekuphazamiseni uchungechunge lokudlulisela kusuka ezikhungweni zezilwane nakubantu abafakwe igciwane kuya ezifuyweni ezicasulayo futhi ivame ukuphelelisa ukwelashwa okulwa namagciwane ekulweni nezifo ezibangelwa amagciwane amasha.
Kwenziwe imizamo yokuthuthukisa imithi yokugoma esekelwe ku-S protein ukuze kukhiqizwe ama-antibody angenabungozi isikhathi eside futhi anamandla kanye/noma ukuvikelwa komzimba ngokumelene ne-SARS-CoV.
Imithi yokugoma ephilayo eyehlisiwe iye yahlolwa ezinhlotsheni zezilwane ze-SARS.
Nokho, ngaphambi kokuba kuqale ucwaningo lwezokwelapha, kusadingeka ukuba kuqinisekiswe ukuthi lezi zithako zokugoma zisebenza kanjani kubantu asebekhulile nasezimodeleni ezibulalayo nokuthi zivikela kanjani ekungenweni igciwane lezilwane.
Lokhu kungenzeka kungenxa yokuthi i-SARS yafa eminyakeni engu-17 edlule futhi akukho muntu omusha obikwayo kusukela lapho.
Ngokuphambene, amacala athile namaqoqo e-MERS ayaqhubeka eqhubeka eMpumalanga Ephakathi futhi asakazekela kwezinye izifunda ngenxa yokungapheli kwemithombo yezilwane ezindaweni ezihlala abantu.
Kuye kwasungulwa amasu okugonana ne-MERS kusetshenziswa igciwane elingenamsebenzi, i-DNA plasmids, ama-vector egciwane, ama-nanoparticle, izinhlayiya ezifana negciwane kanye nama-protein anezinhlanganisela futhi amanye aye ahlolwe kumamodeli ezilwane.
Ukuthuthukiswa komuthi wokugoma ophephile futhi osebenzayo ngokumelene ne-SARS-CoV-2 kubantu abangenayo imithi elwa namagciwane kuwumsebenzi ophuthumayo futhi obalulekile wokulawula lesi sifo esiqhubekayo.
Nokho, kunzima ukunqoba ubunzima ngenxa yesikhathi eside (isilinganiso sezinyanga ezingu-18) esidingekayo ekuthuthukisweni komuthi wokugoma kanye nokuguquguquka okunamandla kwama-CoV.
Njengesifo esisha, i-COVID-19 isanda kuqala ukuveza inkambo yayo egcwele ezigulini eziningi.
Ezimweni eziningi, iziguli zingalulama kancane kancane ngaphandle kwemiphumela emibi.
Nokho, ngokufana ne-SARS ne-MERS, i-COVID-19 nayo ihlotshaniswa nokugula kakhulu nokufa ezigulini ezinezigameko ezinzima.
Ngakho-ke, ukwakha imodeli yokulinganisa lesi sifo kubalulekile ukuze izinhlangano zezempilo zibeke izinsizakalo zazo kuqala, ikakhulukazi ezindaweni ezinezidingo ezincane.
Ngokusekelwe ezifundweni zomtholampilo ezike zabikwa kuze kube manje, lezi zinto ezilandelayo zingathinta noma zihlobene nesibikezelo seziguli ze-COVID-19 (Ithebula (Ithebula33)):
Ubudala: Ubudala bube yisici esibaluleke kakhulu ekuboneni ukuthi i-SARS ingenzeka, okuyiqiniso naku-COVID-19.
I-COVID-19 yenzeke kakhulu kubantu abaneminyaka engu-30-65 kanti abangu-47.7% balabo bagulayo babephezu kweminyaka engu-50 ocwaningweni lwezigameko ezingu-8,866 njengoba kuchaziwe ngenhla.
Iziguli ezazidinga ukunakekelwa okujulile zazinamathuba amaningi okuba nezifo ezihambisana nazo nezinkinga futhi zazineminyaka emide kakhulu kunalezo ezazingenazo (ngeminyaka engu-66 uma kuqhathaniswa no-51), okusikisela ukuthi iminyaka iyisici esichaza umphumela weziguli ze-COVID-19.
Ubulili: I-SARS-CoV-2 ithelele amadoda amaningi kunabesifazane (0.31/100,000 uma kuqhathaniswa no-0.27/100,000), njengoba kuchaziwe ngenhla.
Ukugula okuhambisana nokugula: Iziguli ezine-COVID-19 ezidinga ukunakekelwa okujulile kungenzeka kakhulu ukuthi zizoba nokulimala kwenhliziyo okukhulu kanye ne-arrhythmia.
Izigameko zenhliziyo nazo zaba imbangela eyinhloko yokufa kweziguli ze-SARS.
Kubikwe ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 nayo ingabopha kuma-cholangiocytes ane-ACE2, okungaholela ekungasebenzini kahle kwesibindi ezigulini ze-COVID-19.
Kuyaphawuleka ukuthi iminyaka yobudala nesifo esiyimbangela kuhlobene kakhulu futhi kungase kuphazamise omunye nomunye.
Imiphumela ye - laboratory engavamile: Izinga le - C-reactive protein (CRP) egazini libonisa ubukhulu bokudumba noma ukulimala kwezicubu futhi kuye kwaphakanyiswa ukuthi kungaba isici esingase sibonise ukuthi umuntu uyagula yini, ukuthi uyaphendula yini ekwelashweni, nokuthi ekugcineni usuke esephinde waphila.
Kuye kwaphinde kwaphakanyiswa ukuthi izinga le-CRP lihlobene nobunzima kanye nesibikezelo se-COVID-19.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ukwanda kwe- lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), i- aspartate aminotransferase (AST), i- alanine aminotransferase (ALT), ne- creatine kinase (CK) nakho kungasiza ekubikezeleni umphumela.
La ma-enzyme abonakaliswa kakhulu ezingxenyeni eziningi, ikakhulukazi enhliziyweni nasesibindi, futhi akhululwa lapho izicubu zilimala.
Ngakho, ziyizibonakaliso ezivamile zokungasebenzi kahle kwenhliziyo noma kwesibindi.
Izimpawu ezinkulu zomtholampilo: Ukuhlolwa kwe-X-ray yesifuba nokuthuthuka kwezimpawu zomtholampilo kufanele kubhekwe kanye nezinye izinto zokubikezela imiphumela nezinkinga ze-COVID-19.
Ukusetshenziswa kwama-steroid: Njengoba kuchaziwe ngenhla, ama-steroid ayizinto ezenza umuntu angakwazi ukuzimela ezivame ukusetshenziswa njengendlela yokwelapha izifo ezithathelwanayo ukuze kuncishiswe ukulimala okubangelwa ukuvuvukala.
Njengoba kwakusetshenziswa kakhulu ama-corticosteroid amaningi ezigulini ezinesifo se-SARS esibi kakhulu, abaningi abasinda babhekana ne-osteonecrosis ye-vascular eyayibangela ukukhubazeka okuhlala njalo nokuphila okuphansi.
Ngakho-ke, uma kunesidingo, ama-steroid kufanele asetshenziswe ngemithamo emincane futhi isikhathi esifushane ezigulini ze-COVID-19.
Ukucindezeleka kwengqondo: Njengoba kuchaziwe ngenhla, ngesikhathi kubhebhetheka i-COVID-19, iziguli eziningi zabhekana nokucindezeleka okungavamile njengoba zazivame ukubekezelela isikhathi eside sokuvalelwa zodwa nokungaqiniseki okukhulu futhi zabona ukufa kwamalungu omndeni aseduze kanye neziguli ezikanye nazo.
Kubalulekile ukunikeza iseluleko esingokwengqondo nokusekela isikhathi eside ukuze kusizwe lezi ziguli ukuba ziphinde zibuyele ekuphileni okuvamile.
Ngokwezifundo zabantu kuze kube manje, i-COVID-19 ibonakala inezici ezihlukile ze-epidemiological kune-SARS.
Ngaphezu kokuphindaphinda emgodini ophansi wokuphefumula, i-SARS-CoV-2 ingaphindaphinda ngokuphumelelayo emgodini ophezulu wokuphefumula futhi ibangele izimpawu ezincane noma zingabi bikho esigabeni sokuqala sokutheleleka, okufana namanye ama-CoV abangela imikhuhlane evamile.
Ngakho-ke, iziguli ezithelelekile esigabeni sokuqala noma esikhathini sokukhulelwa zingakhiqiza inani elikhulu legciwane phakathi nemisebenzi yansuku zonke, okubangela ubunzima obukhulu ekulawuleni ubhadane.
Nokho, ukutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV kwakubhekwa njengokwenzeka lapho iziguli zigula kakhulu, kuyilapho ukutheleleka okuningi kungenzeki esigabeni sokuqala.
Ngakho-ke, ukuqubuka kwamanje kwe-COVID-19 kuyingozi kakhulu futhi kunzima kakhulu ukulawula kunokuqubuka kwe-SARS.
Okwamanje kwenziwa imizamo emikhulu eChina kuhlanganise nokuvalwa kweWuhan namadolobha azungezile kanye nokuvalelwa kwabantu bodwa okuqhubekayo cishe kwabo bonke abantu ngethemba lokuqeda ukudluliselwa kwe-SARS-CoV-2.
Nakuba lezi zenzo ziye zalimaza kakhulu umnotho nezinye izingxenye zezwe, inani leziguli ezintsha liyancipha, okubonisa ukuthi ubhadane luyehla.
Ukuqagela okunethemba kakhulu ukuthi lesi sifo sizophela ngoMashi kanti isigaba sokwehla sizothatha izinyanga ezingu-3-4.
Nokho, abanye ochwepheshe abanalo ithemba.
