Nokho, ngokuvalelwa ngokuqinile nokuhlukaniswa, ekugcineni lesi sifo siye salawulwa.
Kungenzeka, ngokufana ne-SARS-CoV, ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ingase ibe buthaka ngokutheleleka futhi ekugcineni iphele noma ibe igciwane elincane elidala izifo eliphila nabantu.
Ukuqhathaniswa kwesifo i-COVID-19 nesifo i-SARS ne-MERS kunikezwa ngezansi (Umdwebo (Umdwebo 55)).
