Indlela yokuqala yokuzivikela engasetshenziswa ukunciphisa ingozi yokutheleleka ukugqoka izifihla-buso; kokubili ukusetshenziswa kwezifihla-buso zokuhlinza kanye nezifihla-buso zokuphefumula ze-N95 (uchungechunge # 1860s) kusiza ukulawula ukusabalala kwamagciwane.
Amaski obuso avimbela amaconsi aketshezi avela kumuntu ongaba negciwane ukuba ahambe emoyeni noma anamathele ezintweni, lapho angadluliselwa khona kwabanye.
Nokho, ama-mask angu-N95 kuphela (uchungechunge # 1860s) angavikela ekuphefumuleni ama-virion amancane njengama-10 kuya ku-80 nm, kanti ama-virion angu-5% kuphela akwazi ukungena ngokuphelele; i-SARS-CoV-2 ifana ne-SARS-CoV ngosayizi futhi womabili anobude obungaba ngu-85 nm.
Njengoba izinhlayiya zingangena ngisho naseziphongweni zokuhlinza ezinhlanu ezihlanganiswe ndawonye, abahlinzeki bezempilo abasebenzelana ngqo neziguli kumelwe bagqoke iziphongosi ze-N95 (uchungechunge # 1860s) kodwa hhayi iziphongosi zokuhlinza.
Ngaphezu kwamamaski, abahlinzeki bezempilo kufanele bagqoke izingubo zokuzihlukanisa ukuze banciphise ukuthintana namagciwane.
Amagciwane angathinta umuntu futhi ngamehlo.
NgoJanuwari 22, 2020, udokotela watheleleka nge-SARS-CoV-2 nakuba wayegqoke imaski ye-N95; kungenzeka ukuthi leli gciwane langena emzimbeni wakhe ngamehlo akhe avuvukile.
Ngakho, abahlinzeki bezokwelapha kufanele bafake nezivikelo zobuso ezibonakala kahle noma izibuko zokugada lapho besebenza neziguli.
Emphakathini jikelele ezindaweni ezithintekile noma ezingase zithinteke, kunconywa kakhulu ukuba wonke umuntu ageze izandla ngensipho yokubulala amagciwane kaningi kunokujwayelekile, azame ukuhlala endlini ukuze azihlukanise futhi anciphise ukuxhumana nabantu abangase babe negciwane.
Abantu babhekwa njengokude nesiguli ngamamitha amathathu.
Lezi zinyathelo ziyizindlela eziphumelelayo zokunciphisa ingozi yokutheleleka kanye nokuvimbela ukusabalala kwegciwane.
Nakuba i-SARS-CoV-2 yafika njenge-virus entsha emhlabeni wesintu, ukufana kwayo okuphezulu ne-SARS-CoV njengoba kwabikwa ngo-7 Januwari 2020 kufanele kube kwabangela ukuba iChina iqaphe kakhulu ngokususelwa enkumbulweni yayo ejulile yokuqubuka kwe-SARS ngo-2003.
Nokho, kwaze kwaba ngomhlaka-19 Januwari 2020 lapho umqondisi we-Center of Disease Control of Wuhan eduduza izakhamuzi ngokuthi leli gciwane elisha linegciwane elincane futhi alinakho ukuzala phakathi kwabantu nokuthi akuyona inkinga ukuvimbela nokuthintwa kwalesi sifo.
Lo myalezo wakhulula kakhulu ukushaqeka komphakathi, ikakhulukazi lapho izwe lonke lilungiselela uMkhosi Wentwasahlobo, futhi isikhathi esibucayi sokubamba lesi sifo ngezinga laso elincane eWuhan saphelelwa yisikhathi.
Izinhlangano ezilawula izifo eChina zingase zithathe lesi sifundo esinzima futhi zenze intuthuko ebalulekile esikhathini esizayo.
Ngokwesibonelo, la ma-ejensi kufanele (1) aqaphele kakhudlwana lapho enza izimemezelo zomphakathi njengoba wonke amazwi abalulekile ezakhamuzini futhi angashintsha isimo sazo sengqondo nezinqumo; (2) abe abhekene kakhulu futhi asabele emyalezweni engavamile evela emtholampilo kunokuba alinde imibiko esemthethweni evela kodokotela noma ezikhulwini; (3) abe alinganisela kakhudlwana ukuze aqede ubhadane olungaba khona esigabeni salo sokuqala kunokuba azame ukududuza umphakathi; futhi (4) akhiphe izikhathi eziningi imihlangano eqondiswe kubantu futhi ephumelelayo yokwandisa ukuqwashisa komphakathi ngezifo eziwumqedazwe futhi ahlole futhi athuthukise isimiso sokuphendula somphakathi ngezikhathi ezithile.
Ukuqubuka kwe-COVID-19 okubangelwa igciwane elisha i-SARS-CoV-2 kwaqala ekupheleni kukaDisemba 2019.
Esikhathini esingaphansi kwezinyanga ezimbili, isakazeke kulo lonke elaseChina nakwamanye amazwe acishe abe ngu-50 emhlabeni wonke ngesikhathi sokubhala lokhu.
Njengoba leli gciwane lifana kakhulu ne-SARS-CoV futhi nezimpawu zifana phakathi kwe-COVID-19 ne-SARS, ukuqubuka kwe-COVID-19 kudale umuzwa wokuthi i-SARS iyaphinda.
Nokho, kunokwehluka okuphawulekayo phakathi kwe-COVID-19 ne-SARS, okuyisidingo ekuvimbeleni lesi sifo nasekwelashweni kweziguli.
I-COVID-19 ithinta abantu asebekhulile kakhulu kunentsha futhi iningi lamadoda kunabesifazane, futhi izinga lobunzima nokufa nalo liphakeme kubantu asebekhulile kunentsha.
I-SARS inezinga lokufa eliphakeme kune-COVID-19 (10.91% uma kuqhathaniswa no-1.44%).
Iziguli ze-COVID-19 zidlulisela leli gciwane ngisho nalapho zingenayo imithelela kuyilapho iziguli ze-SARS zivame ukwenza kanjalo lapho zigula kakhulu, okubangela ubunzima obukhulu kakhulu ekuvimbeleni ukusabalala kwe-COVID-19 kune-SARS.
Lokhu kuchaza ngokwengxenye ukuthi kungani i-SARS-CoV-2 isakazeka ngokushesha okukhulu futhi kabanzi kune-SARS-CoV.
Ukuhlolwa kwe-RNA okuvamile kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kungaba okungalungile kwezinye iziguli ze-COVID-19.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, iziguli eziphulukisiwe zingaphinde zibe negciwane.
Lokhu okutholakele kwandisa kakhulu ingozi yokusabalala kwegciwane.
Ngenxa yentuthuko esheshayo ocwaningweni lwe-COVID-19, kusele izinkinga eziningi ezibalulekile okufanele zixazululwe, njengoba zilandelayo:
Ivelaphi i-SARS-CoV-2?
Nakuba kutholakale ukuthi ama-96% ama-genetic homologue phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 nama-CoV amabili afana ne-SARS, asikwazanga ukufinyelela esiphethweni sokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ivela emagundane.
Yisiphi isilwane esadlulisela leli gciwane kubantu lisuka kumuntu owaba yisilwane sokuqala, njengonogwaja?
Ngaphandle kokwazi izimpendulo zezibalo zokuqala nezesibili, ngeke sikwazi ukunqamula ukudluliswa kwegazi, futhi lesi sifo singaphinde siqubuke noma nini.
Nakuba imodeli yamangqamuzana nokuhlolwa kwamakhemikhali okuphilayo kuye kwabonisa ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ibopha ku-ACE2, igciwane lingena kanjani ngqo kumaseli omgwaqo wokuphefumula futhi libangele izinguquko ezilandelayo ze-pathological?
Ingabe leli gciwane liyabopha amangqamuzana akhipha i-ACE2 kwezinye izitho?
Ngaphandle kwezimpendulo ezicacile zale mibuzo, ngeke sikwazi ukuthola isifo ngokushesha nangokunembile nokwelapha ngendlela ephumelelayo.
Lolu bhubhane luyohlala isikhathi esingakanani?
Igciwane liguquka kanjani ngokwemvelo phakathi kokudluliselwa phakathi kwabantu?
Ingabe iyoba ubhadane lomhlaba wonke, iphele njenge-SARS noma ibuye ihlasele ngezikhathi ezithile njengomkhuhlane?
Kubalulekile kodwa kungase kuthathe isikhathi ukufuna izimpendulo zemibuzo engenhla neminye eminingi.
Nokho, kungakhathaliseki ukuthi kudinga izindleko ezingakanani, asinakho okunye esingakwenza ngaphandle kokuwuqeda ngokushesha lo bhubhane futhi sibuyisele ukuphila kwethu esimweni esivamile.
Imvelaphi ye-coronavirus yabantu
Ukuguquka nokuguquguquka kwezakhi zofuzo kuye kwaholela ekuguqukeni ndawonye kwama-coronavirus (i-CoV) nezidumbu zawo, kuhlanganise nabantu, izinkulungwane zeminyaka.
Ngaphambi kuka-2003, kwakwaziwa ukuthi ama-CoV amabili abantu (ama-HCoV) abangela ukugula okulula, njengokukhuhlana okuvamile.
Ukuqubuka kwesifo esibi kakhulu sokuphefumula (i-SARS) nesifo sokuphefumula saseMpumalanga Ephakathi (i-MERS) kuye kwaveza ukuthi ukutheleleka kwe-HCoV kungaba yingozi futhi kusongela ukuphila kangakanani.
Ukuvela kwe-SARS-CoV-2 enkabeni yeChina ekupheleni kuka-2019 kuphinde kwaphakamisa ama-CoVs futhi futhi futhi kwasimangaza ngokudluliseka kwawo okuphezulu kodwa nokunciphisa ukubangela izifo uma kuqhathaniswa ne-SARS-CoV.
Ukutheleleka nge-HCV kuyisifo sezilwane futhi ukuqonda imvelaphi ye-HCVs kungaba usizo olukhulu kithi.
Ama-HCoV amaningi avela emibuthweni lapho engenazifo.
Ama-host reservoir aphakathi kwezinye i-HCoVs nawo ayaziwa.
Ukwazi ukuthi iziphi izilwane eziyimpilo kunomthelela oqondile ekuvimbeleni izifo zabantu.
Ukuhlola ukusebenzisana kwe-CoV-host ezilwaneni kungaveza nokuqonda okubalulekile mayelana ne-CoV pathogenesis kubantu.
Kulokhu kubuyekezwa, siveza ukubuka konke kolwazi olukhona mayelana nama-HCoV ayisikhombisa, kugxilwe emlandweni wokutholakala kwawo kanye nemvelaphi yawo yezilwane nokudluliselwa kwezinhlobo.
Okubalulekile, siqhathanisa futhi siqhathanisa ama-HCoV ahlukahlukene ngombono wokuziphendukela kwemvelo kwegciwane nokuhlanganiswa kabusha kofuzo.
Ukuqubuka kwamanje kwesifo se-COV 2019 (COVID-19) kuxoxwa ngakho kulesi simo.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, izidingo zokushintsha isidumbu ngokuphumelelayo kanye nemiphumela yokuziphendukela kwemvelo kwegciwane ebuhlungwini besifo nazo ziyaqokonyiswa.
Ama-coronavirus (i-CoVs) angawomndeni i-Coronaviridae, ohlanganisa iqembu lama-virus e-RNA anezinhlamvu eziyindilinga, anezinzwa ezihle.
La magciwane ane-genome enkulu kunazo zonke yama-kilobase angu-26 kuya kwangu-32 phakathi kwama-RNA abizwa ngokuthi ama-CoVs ngenxa yokuma kwawo okufana nomqhele ngaphansi kwesibonakhulu se-electron.
Ngokwesakhiwo, ama-CoV anezinhlayiya zofuzo ezingakahlukaniswa ezihlanganyela inhlangano efanayo.
Cishe izingxenye ezimbili kwezintathu zofuzo ziqukethe ama-frame amabili amakhulu avulekile (i-ORF1a ne-ORF1b), ahunyushelwa kuma-pp1a nama-p1ab replicase polyprotein.
Ama-polyprotein ayaqhubeka esebenza ukuze akhiqize amaprotheni angu-16 angenazo izakhiwo, abizwa ngokuthi nsp1~16.
Ingxenye esele ye-genome iqukethe ama-ORF amaprotheni ezakhiwo, kuhlanganise ne-spike (S), i-envelope (E), i-membrane (M) ne-nucleoprotein (N).
Amaprotheni amaningi anezela asezinhlwini ezithile nawo abhalwe izinhlamvu zamakhodi ezizukulwane ezahlukene zama-CoV.
Ngokusekelwe umehluko emgqeni wamaprotheni, ama-CoV ahlukaniswa abe izizukulwane ezine (i-alpha-CoV, i-beta-CoV, i-gamma-CoV ne-delta-CoV), phakathi kwazo izizukulwane ze-beta-CoV ziqukethe ama-HCoV amaningi futhi zihlukaniswe zaba izizukulwane ezine (A, B, C no-D).
Ubufakazi be-Phylogenetic buye babonisa ukuthi iminenke nezilokazane ziwumthombo wofuzo wama-alpha-CoVs nama-beta-CoVs amaningi, kuyilapho izinyoni ziyizindawo eziyinhloko zama-gamma-CoVs nama-delta-CoVs.
Sekuphele izinkulungwane zeminyaka ama-CoV eqhubeka edlula imingcele yezinhlobo futhi amanye avele njengama-pathogen abalulekile kubantu.
Kuze kube manje, ama-CoV ayisikhombisa abantu (ama-HCoV) ayaziwa.
Phakathi kwazo i-HCoV-229E ne-HCoV-NL63 yi-alpha-CoVs.
Amanye ama-beta-CoV ayisihlanu ahlanganisa i-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-HKU1, i-severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus (SARS-CoV), i-Middle East respiratory syndrome coronavirus (MERS-CoV) ne-SARS-CoV-2.
I-HCoV-229E, i-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-HKU1 ne-HCoV-NL63 ngokuvamile zibangela izimpawu ezincane, njengokukhululeka okuvamile kanye/noma isifo sohudo.
Ngokuphambene, i-SARS-CoV, i-MERS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV-2 esanda kutholakala ziwumkhuhlane kakhulu, zibangela ukutheleleka okunzima komgudu ophansi wokuphefumula ezigulini eziningi kakhulu ezinethuba eliphakeme lokuthola i-Acute Respiratory Distress Syndrome (ARDS) kanye nokubonakaliswa okungaphandle kwamaphaphu.
Uhlobo lokuqala lwe-HCoV-229E, i-B814, lwahlukaniswa emgodini wokuphuma ekhaleni weziguli ezinokukhuhlana okuvamile maphakathi nawo-1960.
Kusukela ngaleso sikhathi, ulwazi oluningi lwaqoqwa ngezifundo eziningana nge-HCoV-229E ne-HCoV-OC43, zombili ezibangela izimpawu ezizivimbelayo.
Ngempela, umqondo wawwamukelwe kabanzi wokuthi ukutheleleka ngama-HCoV ngokuvamile akulimazi kuze kuqubuke i-SARS.
Ukuqubuka kwe-SARS okwenzeka ngo-2003 kungenye yezinto ezibhubhisa kakhulu emlandweni wamanje, kwahlasela abantu abangaphezu kuka-8.000 kanti inani labantu ababulawa yilesi sifo cishe liyi-10%.
Eminyakeni eyishumi kamuva, ukuqubuka kweMiddle East respiratory syndrome (MERS) kwabangela ubhadane olungapheli eNhlonhlweni Yase-Arabia futhi lwasakazekela kancane kancane emhlabeni wonke.
I-HCoV entsha ka-2019 (2019-nCoV), kamuva eyabizwa ngokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2, iyimbangela yesifo esiwumshayabhuqe sesifo se-coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), esibulale abantu abangaphezu kuka-3 120 futhi sabulala abantu abangaphezu kuka-91 000 kusukela ngoMashi 3, 2020.
I-alamu ibilokhu ikhala futhi umhlaba kufanele ulungiselele ubhadane lwe-SARS-CoV-2 oluzayo.
Wonke ama-HCoV ayisikhombisa anomsuka wezilwane ovela emathangeni, kumagundane noma ezilwaneni ezifuywayo.
Imigqa eminingi yobufakazi isekela imvelaphi yokuziphendukela kwemvelo yawo wonke ama-HCoV avela emibuthweni, lapho amagciwane azivumelanisa kahle khona futhi engenazo izifo kodwa ebonisa ukwehlukahluka okukhulu kofuzo.
Ubhadane lwe-COVID-19 luye lwaletha izinselelo ezinkulu kwezokwelapha, kwezesayensi, kwezenhlalo nakwezokuziphatha eChina nasemhlabeni wonke.
Ukulandelela imvelaphi ye-zoonotic yama-HCoV kunikeza uhlaka lokuqonda umlando wemvelo, amandla okuqhuba kanye nezici zokunciphisa ukweqa kwezinhlobo.
Lokhu kungaqondisa noma kusize ekufuneni indawo yokugcina, phakathi nendawo kanye nezilwane ezifuywayo ezandisa i-SARS-CoV-2, okuyinto enemiphumela ebalulekile ekuvimbeleni ukuvuza esikhathini esizayo.
Kulesi sibuyekezo siveza ukubuka konke kwemvelaphi yezilwane, ukudluliswa kwezinhlobo kanye ne-pathogenesis yama-HCoV.
Ikakhulukazi, sigqamisa futhi sixoxe ngendaba evamile yokuthi amagciwane omzali we-HCoV ngokuvamile awabangelwa yizifo ezibangelwa izifo emizini yawo yemvelo kodwa aba nezifo ngemva kokudluliselwa kwezinhlobo ezihlukene kumuntu omusha.
Siphinde sihlaziye ukuthambekela kokuvela kwe-HCoV lapho ukwanda kokudluliselwa kwegciwane kuvame ukuhambisana nokwehla kwe-pathogenicity.
Umphumela wokugqashuka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 okuqhubekayo nawo uyaxoxwa kulo mongo.
Ama-CoV ezilwane aye aziwa kusukela ngasekupheleni kwawo-1930.
Ngaphambi kokuhlukaniswa kokuqala kwe-HCoV-229E strain B814 ekukhishwe emakhaleni ezigulini ezazithole umkhuhlane, ama-CoV ahlukahlukene ayehlukanisiwe ezilwaneni ezihlukahlukene ezinegciwane, kuhlanganise ne-turkey, igundane, inkomo, ingulube, ikati nenja.
Emashumini eminyaka adlule, kuye kwabonakala ama-HCoV ayisikhombisa.
Ukufingqa kafushane umlando wokutholakala kwe-HCoV ngokulandelana kwezikhathi (Ithebula 1) kungaba ukwaziswa nokufundisa.
Uhlobo lokuqala lwe-HCoV-229E lwahlukaniswa emathunjini okuphefumula ezigulini ezinesifo sokungenwa yisifo sokuphefumula esiphezulu ngonyaka ka-1966, futhi kamuva lwasetshenziselwa ukukhula emigqeni yamangqamuzana emaphunga e-WI-38.
Iziguli ezinegciwane le-HCoV-229E zaveza izimpawu ezivamile zokupholisa, ezihlanganisa ikhanda, ukuqhaqhazela, ukucasuka nokuhlushwa umphimbo, kanye nomkhuhlane nokukhwehlela okwenzeka emacaleni angu-10 ~ 20%.
Kamuva ngo-1967, i-HCCoV-OC43 yahlukaniswa ekulinyweni kwezitho zomzimba futhi kamuva yadlula ngokuqhubekayo ebuchosheni bamagundane ancelayo.
Izici zokwelashwa kokutheleleka kwe-HCoV-OC43 zibonakala zifana nalezo ezibangelwa i-HCoV-229E, ezingahlukaniseki ngokobufakazi bokutheleleka kwezinye izakhi ezibangela izifo emithambekeni yokuphefumula njengegciwane lomkhuhlane A ne-rhinovirus.
Kokubili i-HCoV-229E ne-HCoV-OC43 zisakazeka emhlabeni wonke, futhi zivame ukudluliselwa kakhulu ngesikhathi sasebusika esimweni sezulu esilinganisiwe.
Ngokuvamile, isikhathi sokukhulelwa kwalezi zigciwane ezimbili singaphansi kwesonto elilodwa, silandelwe isikhathi esicishe sibe amasonto amabili.
Ngokwesifundo esenziwa kubantu abavolontiya, abantu abaphilile ababetheleleke nge-HCoV-229E baba nomkhuhlane omnene.
Bambalwa kuphela iziguli ezinomzimba omncane okwazi ukumelana nemithi elwa namagciwane ezaba nokutheleleka okunzima emithambekeni yokuphefumula engezansi.
I-SARS, eyaziwa nangokuthi i-atypical pneumonia, yayiwumqedazwe wokuqala obhalwe kahle owenziwa yi-HCoV emlandweni wesintu kanti i-etiological agent yi-SARS-CoV, i-HCoV yesithathu etholakele.
Icala lokuqala le-SARS laqala ngasekupheleni kuka-2002 esifundazweni saseGuangdong eChina.
