Kodwa-ke, okwamanje abukho ubufakazi obusekela imvelaphi eqondile ye-pangolin ye-SARS-CoV-2 ngenxa yokwehluka komugqa phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-pangolin SARS-CoV-2-related beta-CoVs.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ibanga eliphakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-RaTG13 liyifushane ngisho kunalelo eliphakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-pangolin SARS-CoV-2-related beta-CoVs.
Indlela yokuziphendukela kwemvelo ye-SARS-CoV-2 emalulwaneni, kuma-pangolin nakwezinye izilwane ezincelisayo kusafanele isungulwe.
Nakuba kutholakale ukufana okuphezulu kakhulu kwe-RBD phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-pangolin, ama-beta-CoV ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2, i-SARS-CoV-2 ne-RaTG13 ahlanganyela ukufana okuphezulu kakhulu kwe-genome-wide sequence.
Kucatshangwa kakhulu ukuthi izinga eliphakeme lokufana phakathi kwama-RBD e-pangolin SARS-CoV-2 ne-SARS-CoV-2 libangelwa ukuguquka okuguquguqukayo okubangelwa ukukhetha.
Isiphakamiso esiphikisayo sisekela ukuhlanganiswa kabusha phakathi kwe-beta-CoV ehlobene ne-pangolin SARS-CoV-2 ne-RaTG13 ohlotsheni lwesithathu lwezilwane zasendle.
Njengamandla ashukumisayo ekuziphendukeleni kwemvelo, ukuhlanganiswa kabusha kuvame kakhulu phakathi kwama-beta-CoV.
Ijaji lisalokhu lizibuza ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ivela kuphi.
Ngaphandle kwama-HCoV anezifo eziningi, kuye kwafundwa nangomsuka wezilwane we-HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-NL63 ne-HCoV-HKU1.
Ubufakazi be-Phylogenetic buye babonisa ukuthi i-HCoV-NL63 ne-HCoV-229E kungenzeka ukuthi zavela kuma-CoVs ama-bat, kuyilapho amagciwane omzali we-HCoV-OC43 ne-HCoV-HKU1 atholakala ezincekwini.
Kubikwe ukuthi i-bat CoV ebizwa nge-ARCoV.2 (i-Appalachian Ridge CoV) etholakala emantini aseNyakatho Melika anemibala emithathu ibonise ukuthi ihlobene kakhulu ne-HCoV-NL63.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, i-HCoV-229E yayihlobene ngokwemvelo nenye i-bat CoV, ebizwa ngokuthi i-Hipposideros/GhanaKwam/19/2008, eyatholakala eGhana, kuyilapho ama-camellid nawo aye asolwa ngokuthi angumninikhaya wayo ophakathi.
Ukuze kucace, ulwazi lwamanje ngemvelaphi yezilwane yama-HCoV aziwayo lufingqwe esithombeni 1 naseThebula 2.
Ukuhlaziywa kwe-phylogenetic kuye kwanikeza ubufakazi bokudluliselwa kwe-HCoVs phakathi kwezinhlobo emlandweni.
Lapho i-HCV-OC43 iwela izinhlobo ukuze igwinye abantu emfuyweni yasekhaya cishe ngo-1890, kwaqoshwa ubhadane lokutheleleka komoya.
Umlando wokudluliselwa kwe-HCoV-229E phakathi kwezinhlobo akucaci kangako.
Kuye kwatholakala ama-alpha-CoVs ama-bat ahlobene kakhulu ne-HCoV-229E.
Phakathi kwazo kukhona i-alpaca alpha-CoV.
Kunobufakazi obuningi obusekela ukudluliselwa kwegciwane elisuka emathangeni liya kubantu ngokuqondile.
Okokuqala, abantu, hhayi ama-alpaca, bangase babe nobudlelwano namalulwane endaweni efanayo.
Kunalokho, abantu basondelene kakhulu nama-alpaca.
Okwesibili, i-HCoV-229E-related bat alpha-CoVs ihlukahlukene futhi ayiyona into edala izifo emantongomane, kuyilapho i-alpaca alpha-CoV yabangela ukuqubuka kwesifo sokuphefumula ezilwaneni ezinegciwane.
Ekugcineni, i-alpaca alpha-CoV ayitholakalanga ezilwaneni zasendle.
Ngakho-ke, akunakugwenywa ukuthi ama-alpaca angathola i-alpha-CoV ehlobene ne-HCoV-229E kubantu.
Eqinisweni, izimvemvane ziwumthombo oqondile wamagciwane abangela izifo kubantu kuhlanganise negciwane le-rabies, igciwane le-Ebola, igciwane le-Nipah negciwane le-Hendra.
Ngakho-ke akumangalisi ukuthi iminenke ingadlulisela i-HCoV-229E kubantu ngokuqondile.
Ngenye indlela, kuyilapho ama-bat alpha-CoVs esebenza njengegciwane le-HCoV-229E, ama-alpaca namakamela e-dromedary angase abe iziphathimandla eziphakathi ezidlulisela amagciwane kubantu, njengoba kunjalo nge-MERS-CoV.
I-MERS-CoV iyisibonelo esihle kakhulu sokudluliselwa kwezinhlobo kusuka emibuthweni kuya kumakamela e-dromedary nasema-dromedary kuya kubantu.
Umsuka wokuziphendukela kwemvelo we-MERS-CoV emalulwaneni waziwa lapho uqala ukuhlolwa futhi waqiniswa futhi yimiphumela eyalandela.
Kusobala ukuthi iminenke inikeza izinhlobo eziningi zamagciwane ezenza kube nokudluliselwa kwezakhi zofuzo phakathi kwezinhlobo.
Ukuphila isikhathi eside, amakoloni agcwele, ukusebenzelana eduze nabantu kanye nekhono elikhulu lokundiza konke kuyizimo ezifanele ukuze iminenke ibe 'ngumshushisi wegciwane' ofanele.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, i-MERS-CoV iye yaqala ukutholakala kumakamela ase-dromedary amashumi eminyaka.
Ijwayele kahle la makamela asuke ekubeni isivakashi esiphakathi nendawo aba isivakashi esizinzile nesinemithombo yemvelo.
I-MERS-CoV ibangela isifo esincane kakhulu futhi igcina izinga lokuguquka kwezinhlobo zezilwane liphansi kakhulu.
Ukusabalala kwayo ngezikhathi ezithile kubantu kwenzeka ngengozi futhi abantu basaqhubeka beyisibambiso se-MERS-CoV njengoba ukudluliswa kwayo kungeke kuqhubeke.
Ngokuphambene nendima yamakamela ekusakazeni i-MERS-CoV, indima yama-pangolin, uma ikhona, ekusakazeni i-SARS-CoV-2 ihlukile.
Ikakhulukazi, i-pangolin beta-CoVs iyingozi kakhulu kuma-pangolin.
Zingaba isivakashi esifile se-SARS-CoV-2 ezihlobene ne-beta-CoV, ezifana nezimpungushe ezimweni ze-SARS-CoV.
Amathuba amaningana okudluliselwa kwe-SARS-CoV-2 phakathi kwezinhlobo kusuka ezilwaneni kuya kubantu kumele aqedwe noma aqedwe ezifundweni ezizayo.
Okokuqala, iminenke ingaba isidlali esiyisigcini segciwane elihlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2 elicishe lifane ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Abantu bangase bahlanganyele imvelo nemikhombe ngokudla inyama noma ngokumba amalahle.
Okwesibili, ama-pangolin angaba enye yezinhlobo eziphakathi nendawo zokukhulisa igciwane elihlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2 elalisanda kwethulwa.
Abantu bayithola leligciwane ngokubulala nangokudla inyama yezilwane ezizingelayo.
Kungenzeka ukuthi izilwane eziningi ezincelisayo kuhlanganise nezilwane zasekhaya ziyayithola i-SARS-CoV-2.
Kuye kwadingeka ukuba kuhlolwe izilwane ezifuywayo nezilwane zasendle ukuze kutholakale ama-antibody.
Okwesithathu, njengoba kushiwo ngenhla, ukuhlanganiswa kabusha nokuzivumelanisa kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kungenzeka kwenzeke ohlotsheni lwesithathu olunokuxhumana namalulwane kanye nama-pangolin.
Ukufuna imvelaphi yezilwane yeSARS-CoV-2 kusaqhubeka.
Ngaphandle kwezinhlobo ezahlukene zezilwane ezihlala kulezi zilwane, kunezici ezintathu eziyinhloko ezihlobene negciwane ezibalulekile ekwenzeni i-CoVs idlule imingcele yezinhlobo.
Okokuqala, izinga labo eliphakeme lokuvela kwezici ze-RNA.
Uma kuqhathaniswa namanye amagciwane e-RNA anentambo eyodwa, izinga lokuguquka kwe-CoV elinganiselwayo lingabhekwa njenge- moderate kuya ku-high ngezinga lokushintshwa eliphakathi kuka-~10-4 ngonyaka endaweni ngayinye 2, kuye ngesigaba sokulungiswa kwe-CoV kumagumbi amasha.
Ama-CoV anebhonuclease elibonisa ukuthi i-exoribonuclease iyasebenza, lapho ukususwa kwayo kuholela ekuguqukeni okukhulu kakhulu nasekunciphiseni noma ngisho nasekungenzeni umsebenzi.
Ngokuthakazelisayo, i-nucleotide analogue i-Remdesivir yaziwa ngokucindezela ukuphindaphindeka kwe-CoV ngokuvimbela le exoribonuclease ne-RNA-dependent RNA polymerase.
I-Remdesivir ingenye yezidakamizwa ezithembisa kakhulu zokulwa ne-SARS-CoV-2 ezizohlolwa ezivivinyweni zomtholampilo.
Noma kunjalo, izinga lokuguquka kwama-CoV licishe libe izikhathi eziyizigidi ezingaphezu kwezamagciwane abamba lezi zigciwane.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, izinga lokushintsha kwama-CoV livame ukuba liphakeme lapho ama-CoV engakwazi ukuzivumelanisa kahle nomuntu owasingatha.
Uma kuqhathaniswa ne-SARS-CoV enesilinganiso esiphakeme sokuguquka kwemvelo, isilinganiso sokuguquka kwemvelo se-SARS-CoV-2 ngokusobala siphansi, okusikisela izinga eliphakeme lokuzivumelanisa nezimo kubantu.
Cishe, sekuyisikhathi eside isilungele esinye isilwane esiseduze nabantu.
Ngaphezu kwe-SARS-CoV-2, lokhu kusebenza naku-MERS-CoV, okuyinto evumelana kahle namakamela e-dromedary.
Ngokwethiyori, akunakwenzeka ukuthi ukugeleza kofuzo kungenza imithi yokugoma ne-antiviral ngokumelene ne-SARS-CoV-2 ingasebenzi ngokushesha.
Okwesibili, i-RNA enkulu ku-CoVs inobuciko obengeziwe ekuguqulweni kwe-genome ukuze kuvele ukuguquka nokwakheka kabusha, ngaleyo ndlela kwandiswe amathuba okuguquka kwezinto eziphilayo phakathi kwezinhlobo, okuzuzisa ukuvela kwama-CoV amasha lapho izimo sezilungile.
Lokhu kusekelwa yizinhlaka eziningi ezivulekile zokufunda kanye nemisebenzi yamaprotheni ehlelwe ngasekupheleni kwe-3‚Ä≤ kwe-genome.
Okwesithathu, ama-CoV ashintsha izifanekiso ngokungahleliwe futhi kaningi ngesikhathi sokuphindaphinda kwe-RNA ngomshini oyingqayizivele wokukopisha nokukhetha.
Esikhungweni esihlanganisa, ukushintshaniswa kwemicu kwenzeka kaningi ngesikhathi sokubhalwa kwe-RNA ye-CoV.
Ama-RNA anobude obuphelele futhi anobubanzi obungaphansi kwe-genome angahlangana kabusha ukuze akhiqize ama-CoV amasha.
Ubufakazi be-phylogenetic bokuthi ukuhlanganiswa kabusha kwemvelo kutholakala kokubili ku-HCoV-HKU1 naku-HCoV-OC43, kanye nasezilwaneni ze-CoV ezinjenge-bat SL-CoV ne-batCoV-HKU9.
Ukuxhumana kwegciwane nesidumbu maqondana nokudluliselwa
Ngaphandle kwezici ezintathu ezibangelwa amagciwane ezichazwe ngenhla, ukusebenzelana kwegciwane nomamukeli wendawo kungesinye isici esiyinhloko esithonya ukudluliselwa kwegciwane phakathi kwezinhlobo.
Lapha, ukuhlanganiswa kabusha kwe-SARS-CoV kuthathwa njengesibonelo esivamile, okwabonisa ubufakazi bokukhethwa okuhle ngesikhathi sezenzakalo zokudluliswa kwezinhlobo.
Ngokusekelwe ekuhlaziyweni kokuqhathanisa phakathi kwama-isolate e-SARS-CoVs yomuntu ne-civet, i-SARS-CoV kucatshangwa ukuthi iyazivumelanisa ngokushesha nezifo ezihlukile, ikakhulukazi ngokuguquka kwe-RBD ye-S protein.
Ngokuvamile, i-RBD ku-protein ye-S ye-CoV ihlangana nomamukeli wamangqamuzana futhi ikhethwa ngokuqinile impendulo yomzimba wamagciwane.
Ku-SARS-CoV, i-RBD ise-amino acid engu-318 kuya ku-510 engxenyeni ye-S1, ebopha i-ACE2 yomuntu kanye nama-coreceptors ayo ukuze ingenele igciwane.
I-RBD ye-SARS-CoV iyakwazi ukubona ama-ACE2 receptors ezilwane ezihlukahlukene, kuhlanganise nelulwane, i-civet, igundane nenja ye-raccoon, okuvumela ukudluliselwa kwegciwane phakathi kwezinhlobo.
Eqinisweni, kwabonwa kuphela izinsalela ezingu-6 zama-amino acid ezahlukene nezama-virus abantu namagundane ku-RBD futhi ezine zazo zikhona emvelweni obopha i-receptor ukuze zisebenze ne-ACE2 receptor.
I-Civet SARS-CoV inezinguquko ze-K479N ne-S487T ku-RBD yayo, okungase kwandise ukuhlobana kokusebenzisana kwe-spike protein ne-human ACE2 receptor.
Ngamanye amazwi, lezi zindawo ezimbili zama-amino acid zingase zibe ezibalulekile ekuthuthukiseni igciwane kubantu.
Kuyaphawuleka ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ihlanganyela ne-SARS-CoV i-receptor efanayo yamangqamuzana.
Umehluko ongu-30% phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-SARS-CoV esikhungweni se-S1 se-protein S ubonisa ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi ukuhlobana kwe-protein yayo ye-S ne-ACE2 yomuntu sekuguqukile.
Ngempela, ucwaningo lwe-cryo-EM lukhombisa ukuhlobana okuphindwe izikhathi ezingu-10 kuya kwezingu-20 kwalokhu kubopha kunalokho okukhona phakathi kwe-ACE2 yomuntu ne-SARS-CoV S protein.
Kuzoba nentshisekelo futhi ukuthola ukuthi ngabe kukhona yini okunye okudingekayo ukuze kudluliswe i-SARS-CoV-2.
Ngokuthakazelisayo, i-HCoV-NL63 nayo ibopha i-ACE2 kodwa ngenxenye ehlukile ye-S.
Kunamanye ama-receptor amaningi e-HCV, njenge-aminopeptidase N ye-HCV-229E, ne-9-O-acetylated sialic acid ye-HCV-OC43.
Zingabuye zibangele ukuguquguquka ngempumelelo kwalezi CoV kubantu ngemva kokudluliselwa kwezinhlobo kusuka ezifuywayo zezilwane.
Ngaphezu kwama-receptors asecellular, umphumela wokudluliselwa kwama-HCoV phakathi kwezinhlobo nawo ulawulwa ezinye izakhi zokuncika nokunciphisa.
Ukuhluka kwalezi zinhlayiya ezihlala phakathi kwabantu nezihlala emathunjini emvelo e-HCoVs njengama-bat, amakamela e-dromedary nezilonda kungase kube umgoqo ekusakazeni phakathi kwezinhlobo.
Ama-HCoV kufanele athathe izakhi zokuncika komninikhaya futhi aphule izakhi zokunqanda umninikhaya ukuze kudluliselwe izilwane ezihlukene ngempumelelo.
Kulokhu, kusamele kutholakale futhi kuchazwe izinto ezinquma ama-molecule kule ndawo ebalulekile yokusebenzisana kwegciwane nesitha.
Ukuhlolwa okungahleliwe kwe-genome-wide kokuncika komgcini kanye nezici zokunciphisa i-SARS-CoV-2 kusetshenziswa ubuchwepheshe besimanje be-CRISPR kungase kube nemiphumela emihle.
Ukuvela kwama-HCoV amasha: ukubuyela endaweni yokuqala
Ukuhlukahluka kwama-bat CoVs kunikeza amathuba amaningi okuvela kwama-HCoV amasha.
Ngalo mqondo, ama-bat CoVs asebenza njengegciwane le-HCoVs.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ukuguquka okusheshayo nokuhlanganiswa kabusha kofuzo nakho kuyasishukumisela ukuba i-HCoV iguquke futhi kuyisinyathelo esibalulekile kule nqubo.
Ngokwesibonelo, ukuthola noma ukulahlekelwa izakhi zofuzo ezintsha ezifaka amaprotheni kunamandla okuguqula kakhulu ama-phenotypes egciwane.
Phakathi kwamaprotheni e-SARS-CoV, i-ORF8 kucatshangwa ukuthi ibalulekile ekuzivumelaniseni nabantu, njengoba kwahlukaniswa amagciwane emibungu ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV kodwa kwatholakala ukuthi abhala amaprotheni e-ORF8 ahlukene.
Kuye kwatholakala ukuthi i-SARS-CoVs inezici ezibonisa ukuchithwa kwama-nucleotide angu-29 ezihlukaniswe ngokwahlukana ekuqaleni kobhadane kubantu.
Lokhu kususwa kwe-ORF8 kuhlukanisa i-ORF8a ne-ORF8b futhi kucatshangwa ukuthi kuyinguquko eguquguqukayo ekhuthaza ukushintshaniswa kwamagumbi.
Ngaphandle kwalokho, i-SARS-CoV inomlando wokuphinda ihlanganiswe kabusha nemindeni ye-alpha ne-gamma-CoVs, lapho kwabonakala khona inani elikhulu lezindawo ezincane eziphinda zihlanganiswe kabusha ku-RNA-dependent RNA polymerase.
Izindawo zokuhlanganisa kabusha nazo zabonwa ku-nsp9, iningi le-nsp10, nezingxenye ze-nsp14.
Ngokufanayo, kuye kwaboniswa ukuthi ubhadane lwe-MERS-CoV lwaba nezimo zokuhlanganisa kabusha phakathi kwemindeni ehlukene, okwenzeka emakameleni aseSaudi Arabia.
Ngaphandle kwe-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV, izenzakalo zokuhlanganisa kabusha ziye zabonwa nakwezinye i-HCoV, lapho i-HCoV ihlangana khona kabusha namanye ama-CoV ezilwane kumagciwane awo angenazo izakhi zofuzo.
Kufanele kuqashelwe nokuthi ukukhetha okwenziwe umuntu kungabangela izinguquko ezingahlosiwe ku-genome yegciwane, cishe okuwumphumela wokukhulula amagciwane ekucindezelweni okukhethwayo, njengokusetshenziswa isimiso somzimba sokuzivikela komzimba.
Isibonelo salokhu ukulahleka kwe-ORF4 egcwele ku-HCoV-229E prototype strain, ngenxa yokususwa kwama-nucleotide amabili.
Nakuba i-ORF4 engaphazanyisiwe ingabonwa kumagciwane ama-bat namakamela ahlobene ne-HCoV-229E, i-alpaca alpha-CoV ibonisa ukufakwa kwe-nucleotide eyodwa, okuholela ekushintsheni kwesimo.
Okokugcina kodwa okungasho lutho, ukuvela kwama-HCoV amasha nakho kuqhutshwa ingcindezi yokukhetha kumagumbi awo okuhlala.
Kwabonakala izimpawu ezingenayo izimpawu noma ezincane kuphela lapho iminenke yayitheleleke ngama-Covs, okukhombisa ukuguquguquka phakathi kwama-Covs neminenke.
Kwabonakala ukuthi izimbungulu zilungele kahle i-CoVs ngokwakheka komzimba nangokomzimba.
Ngokwesibonelo, amaphutha ekusebenzeni kwempendulo evikela ukuvuvukala emalulwaneni anciphisa ngempumelelo isifo esibangelwa ama-CoV.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, umsebenzi wamangqamuzana abulala ngokwemvelo emalulwaneni ucindezelwa ngenxa yokwehliswa kwe-NKG2/CD94 receptor yamangqamuzana abulala ngokwemvelo kanye nezinga eliphansi lokukhuluma ngama-molecule amakhulu e-histocompatibility complex class I.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, izinga eliphakeme lezinhlobo zomoya-mpilo ezenza ukusabela (i-ROS) ezikhiqizwa ngokusebenza okuphezulu kwe-metabolic kwemikhombe lingavimbela ukuphindaphindeka kwe-CoV futhi lithinte ukuhlolwa kwe-exoribonuclease, ngaleyo ndlela linikeze ingcindezi yokukhetha ukukhiqizwa kwamagciwane anezifo eziningi lapho efakwa kumuntu omusha.
Izinhlobo ze-CoV eziyingozi kakhulu zingase futhi zivele ngokuhlanganiswa kabusha, okuholela ekutholeni amaprotheni amasha noma izici zamaprotheni ukuze zilungele ukusetshenziswa.
Ngakho-ke, akulona iphutha ukuthi ama-HCoV amathathu amasha avele emashumini amabili eminyaka adlule.
Ama-CoV awasiwo amagciwane noma abangela izimpawu ezincane ezihlalweni zawo ezinjengemidlwane namakamela.
Zilokhu zanda ngaphandle kokubangela ukusabela okuqinile komzimba.
Lapha kunemfihlo yokuthi kungani kubonwa abathwali abangabonisi zimpawu nokuthi yini ebangela amacala anzima okuhlasela kwabantu.
Izimpawu ezinzima zibangelwa ikakhulukazi ukuvuselelwa ngokweqile kwempendulo yomzimba yokulwa nezifo kanye nesiphepho se-cytokine lapho lapho impendulo yomzimba yokulwa nezifo iba namandla khona, umonakalo wamaphaphu uba mubi nakakhulu.
Ngokuphambene, kubantu abangenazo izimpawu, impendulo yomzimba iye yahlukaniswa nokuphindaphindwa kwe-CoV.
Isu elifanayo lokuhlukanisa impendulo yomzimba elwa namagciwane lingase libe nemiphumela emihle ekwelashweni kwe-anti-SARS-CoV-2.
Impendulo ye-interferon iqine kakhulu emalulwaneni.
Ngakho-ke, ukuphathwa kwe-interferon yohlobo I okungenani esigabeni sokuqala sokutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kubantu kufanele kube nenzuzo.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ukusebenza kwe-NLRP3 ku-inflammasome emalulwaneni akulungile.
Ngalesi sizathu, ukuvimbela i-NLRP3 inflammasome nge-MCC950 kungase kube usizo ekwelapheni i-COVID-19.
Ukuvela kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kulandela isihloko esijwayelekile lapho i-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV zavela khona.
Nakuba kutholakale i-bat beta-CoV ehlanganyela i-95% ye-nucleotide homology ne-SARS-CoV, kukhona ne-bat-CoV ehlanganyela i-96% ye-nucleotide homology ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Nakuba kutholakale ukuthi izilwane ezinjengezimvubu nezinye ezimakethe zinamagciwane afana ne-SARS-CoV, izidumbu eziphakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 azikaziwa.
Kutholakale ama-Pangolin beta-CoVs afana kakhulu ne-SARS-CoV-2, okusikisela ukuthi ama-pangolin angase abe ngomunye wabanikazi abaphakathi noma ama-Pangolin beta-CoVs angasiza ngezingcezwana zofuzo ezakha inguqulo yokugcina ye-SARS-CoV-2.
Nakuba kusekhona imibuzo, abukho ubufakazi bokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 yenziwe umuntu ngenhloso noma ngengozi.
Ama-CoV abuyele ekukhanyeni ngenxa yokuqubuka kwakamuva kwe-SARS-CoV-2.
Ucwaningo lwama-CoV emibuthweni nakwezinye izilwane lushintshe kakhulu umbono wethu ngokubaluleka kwemvelaphi yezilwane kanye nezindawo ezigcina izilwane ze-HCoVs ekusakazeni kubantu.
Ubufakazi obusakazekayo buye babonisa ukuthi i-SARS-CoV, i-MERS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV-2 zivela emathunjini futhi zidluliselwa kubantu ngezilwane eziphakathi.
Njengoba ukutheleleka nge-SARS-CoV kuvela ekuxhumaneni phakathi kwabantu nezilwane zasemgwaqweni ezimakethe, ukuvala izimakethe ezimanzi nokubulala izilwane zasemgwaqweni lapho bekungaqeda ubhadane lwe-SARS.
Ngokusho okufanayo, ama-pangolin kufanele asuswe ezimakethe ezimanzi ukuze kuvinjelwe ukudluliselwa kwezilwane ngenxa yokuthola imigqa eminingi yama-pangolin beta-CoV ahlobene kakhulu ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Nokho, ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 idluliselwa kanjani kubantu nge-pangolins nezinye izilwane ezincelisayo kusazobonakala ekuhlolweni kwesikhathi esizayo.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, i-MERS-CoV ibikhona emakamela e-dromedary isikhathi eside.
Lezi zimvubu ziyisithuthi esibalulekile futhi ziwumthombo oyinhloko wenyama, ubisi, isikhumba nemikhiqizo yoboya kubantu bendawo.
Zisabalele kulo lonke elaseMpumalanga Ephakathi nase-Afrika.
Ngakho-ke akunakwenzeka ukudela wonke amakamela ukuze kulawulwe i-MERS, njengoba kwenziwa ezimakethe zezilwane zasendle eChina ukuze kuvinjelwe ukusakazeka kwe-SARS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Ukuze kuvinjelwe ukuqubuka okuphindaphindiwe kwe-MERS, kufanele kuthathwe indlela ebanzi yokuthuthukisa imithi yokugoma esebenzayo emelene ne-MERS-CoV yamakamela, kuhlanganiswe nezinye izinyathelo zokulawula ukutheleleka.
Njengoba singakwazi ukuziqeda lezi zigciwane, kungase kuvele izinhlobo ezintsha ezibangela ukuqubuka.
Kunezinhlobo ezihlukahlukene zama-CoV ezinobuthi obungelapheki ezijikeleza endle.
Ikakhulukazi, ama-CoV ama-bat anethuba lokubulala izilwane ahlukahlukene kakhulu.
Kunamathuba amaningi okuthi la ma-CoV ane-zoonotic aguquke futhi ahlanganiswe kabusha, okuholela ekuveleni kwama-CoV amasha adluliseka kakhulu futhi/noma abulalayo kubantu esikhathini esizayo.
Isiko lokudla izilwane zasendle kwezinye izindawo zaseChina kufanele liyekwe ukuze kuncishiswe ukuxhumana okungadingekile phakathi kwabantu nezilwane.
Ngenxa yezinhlupheko ze-SARS, MERS ne-COVID-19, kufanele kube khona ukulungela kangcono kanye nohlelo lokuphendula.
Eqinisweni, amagciwane amaningi abekhona emhlabeni isikhathi eside kakhulu.
Zihlala emithonjeni yazo yemvelo kuze kube yilapho kuvela ithuba lokusabalala.
Nakuba izimbungulu zinezici eziningi ezenza kube lula ukusakazeka kwamagciwane, amathuba okuba abantu baxhumane nezimbungulu nezinye izilwane zasendle angancishiswa uma abantu befundiswa ukuba bangazihlanganisi nazo.
Ukuqapha okuqhubekayo ezincelisayo kuyadingeka ukuze kuqondwe kangcono imvelo ye-CoVs nezinduna zayo zemvelo, okuyoba usizo ekuvimbeleni ukudluliselwa kwezilwane kubantu kanye nokuqubuka esikhathini esizayo.
Ekuphetheni, indlela ephumelela kunazo zonke yokuvimbela i-zoonosis eyigciwane iwukuba abantu bahlale kude nezindawo eziyindawo yemvelo lapho kunamagciwane agcina izilwane.
Izingcezu eziningana zepuzzle lomsuka we-zoonotic we-SARS-CoV-2 zisalahlekile.
Okokuqala, uma iminenke idlulisela igciwane lomkhulu le-SARS-CoV-2 kuma-pangolin, kuyoba nesithakazelo ukubona ukuthi ngaphansi kwaziphi izimo iminenke nama-pangolin angahlanganyela indawo efanayo yezemvelo.
Okwesibili, uma iminenke idlala indima eqondile ekusakazeni kubantu, kufanele kunqunywe ukuthi abantu bahlangana kanjani neminenke.
Okwesithathu, uma isilwane sesithathu esincelisayo singumnikazi wangempela ophakathi, kufanele kucaciswe ukuthi sisebenzelana kanjani nezinhlobo ezahlukene kuhlanganise nabantu, iminenke nama-pangolin.
Ekugcineni, njengoba izilwane eziningi ezincelisayo kuhlanganise nezilwane zasekhaya zingase zibe nesibopho ku-SARS-CoV-2, kufanele kwenziwe ukuqapha nokutheleleka okuhlolwayo.
Uma kungumbhede, i-pangolin noma esinye isilwane esincelisayo, kulindeleke ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 noma amagciwane ayo angabazali acishe afane nawo azotholakala kumagumbi ayo emvelo esikhathini esizayo.
Ukuqhubeka kophenyo kule ndawo kuzocacisa indlela yokuziphendukela kwemvelo ye-SARS-CoV-2 ezilwaneni, okuzoba nemiphumela ebalulekile ekuvimbeleni nasekulawuleni i-COVID-19 kubantu.
Kuyadingeka ukuvuselela imigomo yokuxilonga i-COVID-19  icala elisolisayo  ne-  icala eliqinisekisiwe 
NgoFebhuwari 6, 2020, ithimba lethu lashicilela umhlahlandlela wokweluleka okusheshayo wokutholakala nokwelashwa kokutheleleka okusha kwe-coronavirus ka-2019-nCoV ka-2019, futhi lo mhlahlandlela wanikeza ulwazi lwethu futhi wenza inkomba enhle yokulwa nalolu bhubhane emhlabeni wonke.
Kodwa-ke, isifo se-coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) yisifo esisha, ulwazi lwethu nokwazi kwethu kuyanda kancane kancane ngokususelwa emiphumeleni yocwaningo oluqhubekayo kanye nokuhlangenwe nakho komkhuba wezokwelapha; ngakho-ke, amasu okuxilonga nokwelashwa nawo ayaqhubeka evuselelwa.
Kulesi sihloko, siphendule omunye wamazwana esiwuphawu lomhlahlandlela wethu futhi sanikeza imigomo yakamuva yokuxilonga ye- "isimo esingasolwayo" kanye "nesimo esiqinisekisiwe" ngokusho kwe- "Diagnosis and Treatment Guidelines for COVID-19" yakamuva (inguqulo yesikhombisa) ekhishwe yi-National Health Committee of the People's Republic of China.
NgoDisemba 2019, i-coronavirus entsha ka-2019 (2019-nCoV) idale ukuqubuka, manje esebizwa ngokusemthethweni ngokuthi isifo se-coronavirus ka-2019 (COVID-19) futhi leli gciwane selibizwa ngokuthi i-severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ngo-11 Mashi 2020, i-WHO yachaza i-COVID-19 njengobhadane.
Ukuze silwe nokutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV-2, ithimba lethu lenze umhlahlandlela wokweluleka okusheshayo futhi ushicilelwe ku-inthanethi kuyi-Military Medical Research ngo-February 06, 2020.
Sekuhehile ukunakwa okukhulu selokhu sashicilelwa.
Nokho, phawula ukuthi i-COVID-19 isifo esisha, ulwazi lwethu luyanda kancane kancane ngokususelwa emiphumeleni yocwaningo oluqhubekayo kanye nokuhlangenwe nakho komkhuba wezokwelapha; ngakho-ke, amasu okuxilonga nokwelashwa nawo ayaqhubeka evuselelwa.
Isibonelo, Imihlahlandlela Yokuxilongwa Nokwelashwa Kwe-COVID-19 ekhishwe yiKomiti Yezempilo Kazwelonke Yase-People's Republic of China (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), phakathi kuka-16 Januwari 2020 kuya ku-3 Mashi 2020, ikhishwe ngezihumusho ezingu-7 kanti ezinye izingqikithi zishintshiwe kakhulu.
Manje umhlahlandlela wethu wathola ukuphawula kukaZhou nabanye, baveza isiphakamiso esilula sokulinganisa esisekelwe ekuhlangenwe nakho kwabo emtholampilo.
Umsebenzi wabo ungeze ubufakazi obusha obubonisa ukuthi lesi siqondiso sisebenza futhi wenza inkomba ebalulekile ngalesi sifo esiwumshayabhuqe emhlabeni wonke.
Siyawuvuma umsebenzi wabo obalulekile futhi sibonga.
Kodwa-ke, umsebenzi wabo udinga ukubuyekezwa ngokuya nge-Diagnosis and Treatment Guidelines yakamuva ye-COVID-19 (Uhlolo lwesikhombisa) kanye nezifundo zakamuva.
Ngokwesiphequluli sesikhombisa (3 Mashi 2020), ukuqinisekisa icala elisolwayo kudingeka kuhlanganiswe noma iyiphi into eyodwa yezici zomlando wezifo eziwumqedazwe kanye nezinto ezimbili ezivezwayo emtholampilo ukwenza ukuhlaziywa okuphelele, noma kudingeka kuhlangatshezwane nezinto ezintathu ezivezwayo emtholampilo uma kungekho mlando ocacile wezifo eziwumqedazwe:
Umlando wezifo: (1) umlando wokuhamba noma wokuhlala edolobheni laseWuhan nasezindaweni ezizungezile, noma eminye imiphakathi lapho kubikwe khona iziguli ze-COVID-19 ezinsukwini ezingu-14 ezedlule ngaphambi kokuqala kwezimpawu; (2) umlando wokuxhumana neziguli ezithathelwanayo ze-SARS-CoV-2 (ezinokuhlolwa kwe-nucleic acid okuyi-positive); (3) umlando wokuxhumana neziguli ezinomkhuhlane noma izimpawu zokuphefumula ezivela edolobheni laseWuhan nasezindaweni ezizungezile, noma eminye imiphakathi lapho kubikwe khona i-COVID-19 ezinsukwini ezingu-14 ezedlule ngaphambi kokuqala kwezimpawu; (4) umlando wokuxhumana neqembu leziguli eziqinisekisiwe (‚â• 2 iziguli ezinomkhuhlane kanye/noma izimpawu zokuphefumula zenzeka kungakapheli amasonto amabili ezindaweni ezincane, njengekhaya, ehhovisi, ekilasini lesikole, njll.).
Izimpawu zokugula: (1) umkhuhlane kanye/ noma izimpawu zokuphefumula; (2) izimpawu zokubonisa ukutheleleka nge-COVID-19; (3) inani lama-cell amhlophe egazi libonisa inani lama-lymphocyte elivamile, elincishisiwe noma elincishisiwe esigabeni sokuqala.
Ukuxilongwa kwecala eliqinisekisiwe kufanele kusekelwe ecaleni elisolwayo kunoma iyiphi into eyodwa yobufakazi obubangela isifo noma i-serological njengoba kulandela: (1) ukuhlolwa kwe-PCR ngesikhathi sangempela okufakazela ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 iyasebenza; (2) ukulandelana kwe-genome yonke yegciwane okubonisa ukufana okuphezulu kwama-coronavirus amasha aziwayo; (3) ukuhlolwa kwe-serum okufakazela ukuthi i-IgM ne-IgG antibody ku-SARS-CoV-2 zisebenza kahle; noma ushintsho lwe-SARS-CoV-2 lwe-IgG antibody kusuka kokungemuhle kuya kokuhle, noma i-titer inyuka izikhathi ezingu- ‚â•4 esigabeni sokululama ngaphezu kwesesigabeni esibucayi.
Siyabona ukuthi ukuhlolwa kwe-PCR ngesikhathi sangempela kwe-nucleic acid emathunjini okuphefumula noma emasampula egazi kwengezwe ezigabeni ezimbili (18 January 2020) nesithathu (22 January 2020).
Ukuhlolwa kwezinto ezibangela izifo esampula legazi kwengezwa kumagazini wesine (27 Januwari 2020) nowesihlanu (8 Februwari 2020); kwathi ubufakazi be-serological bengezwa kumagazini wesikhombisa.
Lezi zinguquko ezisekelwe kubacwaningi zaqhubeka nomsebenzi wokufuna ikhithi yokuxilonga i-nucleic acid efanelekile ukuze kutholakale ukuxilongwa okusheshayo, kanye namasampula avela emithambekeni yokuphefumula kuhlanganise nokutholwa kwegazi, okwandisa ukutholakala kwamasampula ahlukahlukene, futhi kwasekela ukuletha umphumela omuhle we-antibody ethile ezicini eziqinisekisiwe.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, kunobufakazi obuningi obusinxusa ukuba siqaphele ngeziguli ezingavamile ezinezimpawu nezingenayo.
Ngakho-ke, ishadi lokugeleza likaZhou nabanye kufanele libuyekezwe, njengoba behlukanisa umuntu ongenazo izimpawu njengonobungozi obuncane.
Uhlelo lokulinganisa kufanele futhi luqinisekiswe eminye imikhuba nasemicwaningweni.
Ekuphetheni, sinethemba lokuthi kuzoba nobufakazi obengeziwe obuqondile futhi sicela abafundi ukuba banikeze imibono yabo.
Ukuze kutholakale ukuthi umuntu "usolwa" yini nokuthi "usolwa" yini, siphakamisa ukuthi bathole futhi balandele iziqondiso zakamuva zezwe lakubo.
Ithimba lethu lizoyibuyekeza ngesikhathi esifanele imihlahlandlela yethu ukuze linikeze usizo.
IBangladesh ibika ukufa kwabantu abasha abahlanu ngenxa ye-COVID-19, okuyisibalo esiphezulu nsuku zonke.
Izolo, iBangladesh iqinisekise ukufa kwabantu abasha abahlanu ngenxa ye-COVID-19 ngalolo suku.
