Izitolo e-Australia zinciphisa imingcele yephepha langasese ngokuthengiselana
NgeSonto nangoMgqibelo kusihlwa, izitolo zase-Australia iWoolworths neColes zehlisa imikhawulo yazo yokuthenga iphepha langasese yaba amaphakethe amabili nelilodwa ngokuthengiselana kuzo zonke izitolo ezingeni likazwelonke, ngokulandelana.
I-ALDI nayo yafaka umkhawulo wephakethe elilodwa, ngoMsombuluko.
Le mingcele yayithunyelwe njengemiyalezo ekhasini, nasemakhasini e-Facebook ezinkampani.
Kubikwa ukuthi abathengi babelokhu bethengisa ngenxa yokwesaba i-COVID-19 uma kwenzeka abantu bedinga ukuzihlukanisa.
NgoLwesithathu, iWoolworths nayo yanciphisa ukuthengwa kwephepha langasese ukuze lithunyelwe ekhaya libe yiphakethe elilodwa ngomyalo ngamunye.
Lezi zinguquko zalandela ukuvinjelwa kwangaphambilini kwepakethe ezine ngokuthengiselana okwenziwa yiWoolworths neColes ngoMashi 4 no-5 ngokulandelana.
"I-Coles, ekukhululweni kwayo kwabezindaba ngoMashi 8, yabika ukuthi njengoba kunomkhawulo wamaphakethe amane, "izitolo eziningi zisathengisa kungakapheli ihora elilodwa", futhi yabiza lesi sidingo ngokuthi "asizange sibe khona", kanti i-ALDI, kokuthunyelwe kwayo kuFacebook ngoLwesibili, yakubiza ngokuthi "akulindelwe".
"Ukuthengiswa kwehle kakhulu ngesonto eledlule, ngokusho komkhulumeli weWoolworths".
