URussell Zimmerman, umqondisi ophethe we-Australian Retailers Association, wathi abathengisi bazama ukuqoqa izimpahla, kodwa imingcele yomkhandlu wendawo ngesikhathi sokulethwa kwamaloli yenza kube nzima.
Ulindele izindleko zokukhiqiza ezikhuphukayo, njengoba abahlinzeki bezama ukuhlangabezana nesidingo, kanye nokunciphisa izipesheli.
