Ngokufanayo, ngaphandle kwe-Australia, ngeSonto kusihlwa esitolo esikhulu saseBrithani i-online i-Ocado sabonwa sinciphisa ukuthengwa kwephepha langasese lika-Andres ukuba amaphakethe amabili anemiqulu engu-12.
Inhlangano Yezempilo Yomhlaba Wonke Imemezela Ukuthi I-COVID-19 Iyisibhicongo
NgoLwesithathu, iWorld Health Organization (WHO) yamemezela ukuthi ukuqubuka kwe-COVID-19 okuqhubekayo  isifo esibangelwa i-coronavirus SARS-CoV-2  kuyisifo esiwumqedazwe.
"Nakuba igama elithi "ubhadane" libhekisela kuphela ekutheni isifo sesisakazeke kangakanani, hhayi ukuthi amacala athile ayingozi kangakanani, i-WHO yaphawula isidingo sokushayela ohulumeni esenzweni:"
Wonke amazwe asengantshintsha inkambo yalesi sifo.
Uma amazwe ethola, ehlola, elapha, ehlukanisa, elandelela futhi ehlanganisa abantu bawo ekuphenduleni, kusho uTedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, uMqondisi-Jikelele we-WHO.
Sikhathazeke kakhulu ngezinga eliyingozi lokusabalala nobunzima kanye nezinga eliyingozi lokungenzi lutho.
"Ngokusho kukaDkt. Tom Frieden, owayengumqondisi we-United States' Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, lesi sifo esiwumqedazwe "asinaso isandulela".
"Uthe, emazwini ashicilelwe yi-CNN ngoFebhuwari, ""ngaphandle komkhuhlane, alikho elinye igciwane lokuphefumula eliye latholakala kusukela ekuveleni kwalo kuze kube yilapho lisakazeka emhlabeni wonke".
"UGhebreyesus waveza umbono ofanayo, ethi ""asikaze sibone ubhadane olubangelwa igciwane le-coronavirus""".
"Waqhubeka, ""futhi asikaze sibone ubhadane olungalawulwa ngesikhathi esifanayo. """
Isimo esisha njengobhadane silandela isinqumo se-WHO ngoJanuwari sokumemezela lesi sifo njengesifo esiphuthumayo sezempilo yomphakathi esikhathaza amazwe omhlaba.
"Umqondisi we-United States' National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Disease, uDkt. Anthony Fauci, wathi mayelana nalolu bhubhane, ""ngokuyinhloko, luzobe lushabalala". "
NgoLwesine, i-Associated Press yabika ukuthi okungenani kwakunezigameko ezingu-126 000 ze-COVID-19 emhlabeni wonke, okwaholela ekufeni kwabantu abangaphezu kuka-4 600.
I-COVID-19 iyisifo esiwumshayabhuqe esibangelwa i-severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Lesi sifo satholakala eWuhan, eChina, ngoDisemba 2019, samenyezelwa njenge-Public Health Emergency of International Concern ngoJanuwari 30, 2020, futhi samenyezelwa njengobhadane ngoMashi 11, 2020.
Kusukela mhla ziyi-10 Ephreli 2020, cishe abantu abayizigidi ezingu-1.61 abatheleleke nge-COVID-19 babikwa emazweni angu-210 nasezifundeni, okuholele ekufeni kwabantu abangaba ngu-97 000.
Abantu abangaba ngu-364 000 baye balulama.
Izinga lokufa kwabantu eChina lilinganiselwa ku-4%, kanti emhlabeni wonke lisukela ku-13,04% e-Algeria kuya ku-0,08% eNew Zealand.
Izimpawu ezivamile zihlanganisa umkhuhlane, ukukhwehlela nokuphefumula kanzima.
Izinkinga zingahlanganisa i-pneumonia ne-acute respiratory distress syndrome.
Isikhathi esivela ekuchayekeni kuze kuqale izimpawu ngokuvamile cishe izinsuku ezinhlanu, kodwa singase sihluke phakathi kwezinsuku ezimbili nezingu - 14.
Awukho umuthi wokugoma noma ukwelashwa okuqondile okulwa namagciwane.
Ukwelashwa okuyisisekelo ukwelashwa okubonisa izimpawu kanye nokweseka. Izinyathelo zokuvimbela ezinconywayo zihlanganisa ukugeza izandla, ukumboza umlomo lapho ukhwehlela, ukugcina ibanga kwabanye abantu, nokuqapha nokuzihlukanisa kubantu abasola ukuthi banegciwane.
Iziphathimandla emhlabeni wonke ziye zaphendula ngokumisa imikhawulo yokuhamba, ukuvalelwa, isikhathi sokubuya ekhaya, ukulawula izingozi emsebenzini nokuvala izikhungo.
Lolu bhubhane luholele ekuphazamisekeni okukhulu kwezomnotho nomphakathi emhlabeni wonke, ukuhlehliswa noma ukukhanselwa kwemicimbi yezemidlalo, yenkolo, yezombusazwe neyesiko, kanye nokuntuleka kokuthengwa kwempahla okuye kwabangelwa ukuthenga okubangelwa ukwethuka.
Izikole namanyuvesi ziye zavalwa ezweni lonke noma endaweni ethile emazweni angu-193, okuye kwathinta cishe amaphesenti angu-99,4 abantu abafundi emhlabeni.
Ukwaziswa okungamanga ngaleli gciwane kuye kwasakazeka ku-inthanethi, futhi kuye kwaba nezigameko zokuzonda abantu bakuleli kanye nokucwaswa kwabantu baseChina, abanye abantu abavela eMpumalanga naseNingizimu-mpumalanga ye-Asia, kanye nabanye abavela ezindaweni ezinezimo eziphawulekayo zegciwane.
Ngenxa yokunciphisa ukuhamba nokuvalwa kwezimboni ezisindayo, kuye kwaba nokwehla kokungcoliswa komoya nokukhishwa kwekhabhoni.
Iziphathimandla zezempilo eWuhan, eChina (inhloko-dolobha yesifundazwe saseHubei) zabika ngeqembu lamacala okuqubuka komoya anembangela engaziwa ngoDisemba 31, 2019, futhi kwaqalwa uphenyo ekuqaleni kukaJanuwari 2020.
Izimo eziningi zaziphathelene neHuanan Seafood Wholesale Market ngakho-ke leligciwane kucatshangwa ukuthi linomsuka wezilwane.
Igciwane elabangela lesi sifo laziwa ngokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2, igciwane elisanda kutholakala elihlobene kakhulu ne-bat coronaviruses, i-pangolin coronaviruses, ne-SARS-CoV. Umuntu wokuqala owaziwayo owayenemiphumela yalesi sifo kamuva watholakala ukuthi wagula ngo-1 Disemba 2019, futhi lowo muntu wayengenabo ubudlelwane obubonakalayo neqembu lasemakethe emanzi kamuva.
Eqenjini lokuqala lamacala abikwa ngoDisemba 2019, kwatholakala ukuthi izingxenye ezimbili kwezintathu zazinokuxhumana nemakethe.
Ngo-13 Mashi 2020, umbiko ongaqinisekisiwe ovela eSouth China Morning Post wasikisela ukuthi icala elaqala ngo-17 Novemba 2019, kumuntu oneminyaka engu-55 ovela esifundazweni saseHubei, kungenzeka ukuthi laliyokuqala. Ngo-26 Febhuwari 2020, i-WHO yabika ukuthi, njengoba kubikwa ukuthi amacala amasha ancipha eChina kodwa anda ngokungazelelwe e-Italy, e-Iran naseNingizimu Korea, inani lamacala amasha ngaphandle kweChina lase lidlulile inani lamacala amasha ngaphakathi kweChina okokuqala ngqa.
Kungaba nokumenyezelwa okuncane kakhulu kwamacala, ikakhulukazi phakathi kwalabo abanezimpawu ezincane.
NgoFebhuwari 26, kwakubikwa amacala ambalwa kakhulu kubantu abasha, kanti labo abaneminyaka engu-19 nangaphansi kwakumelwe babe ngu-2.4% wamacala emhlabeni wonke. Umeluleki omkhulu wezesayensi e-United Kingdom, uPatrick Vallance, walinganisela ukuthi u-60% wabantu baseBrithani kwakuzodingeka ukuba bathole igciwane ngaphambi kokuba kutholakale amasosha omhlambi asebenzayo.
Amacala abhekisela enanini labantu abahlolelwe i-COVID-19, futhi okuqinisekiswe ukuthi banesifo ngokusho kwama-protocols asemthethweni.
Kusukela ngoMashi 23, alikho izwe elalihlolwe ngaphezu kuka-3% wabantu balo, futhi amazwe amaningi ayenemigomo esemthethweni yokungahlolwa kwalabo abanezimpawu ezincane kuphela, njenge-Italy, iNetherlands, iSpain neSwitzerland.
Ucwaningo olushicilelwe ngoMashi 16 lwathola ukuthi eChina, kuze kube nguJanuwari 23, kulinganiselwa ukuthi ama-86% abantu abatheleleke nge-COVID-19 ayengakaze atholakale, nokuthi lezi zinkinga ezingekho emthethweni zaziyimbangela yokutheleleka kwezingu-79% zezigameko ezibhalwe phansi.
Ukuhlaziywa kwezibalo okwanyatheliswa ngoMashi 30 kulinganiselwa ukuthi inani labantu abatheleleke e-Italy lalikhulu kakhulu kunamacala abikiwe.
Izilinganiso zokuqala zenombolo eyisisekelo yokuzala kabusha (R0) ye-COVID-19 zazingaba ngu-1.4 kuya ku-2.4.
Ucwaningo olushicilelwe yi-US Center for Disease Control and Prevention luye lwaphetha ngokuthi kungenzeka kube ngu-5.7.
Iningi labantu abane-COVID-19 liyaphiliswa.
Kulabo abangenayo, isikhathi esivela ekubonakaleni kwezimpawu kuze kube sekufeni besingaba phakathi kwezinsuku ezingu-6 nezingu-41, okuvame kakhulu ukuba yizinsuku ezingu-14.
Ngo-Ephreli 10, 2020, cishe abantu abangu-97,000 base bebulewe yi-COVID-19.
EChina, ngoFebhuwari 5, cishe abantu abangu-80% abafa kwakungabantu abaneminyaka engaphezu kwengu-60, kanti abangu-75% babenezimo zempilo ezikhona ngaphambili ezihlanganisa izifo zenhliziyo nesifo sikashukela. Ukubalwa okusemthethweni kwabantu abafa ngenxa yobhadane lwe-COVID-19 ngokuvamile kubhekisela kubantu abafile abahlolwe ukuthi bane-COVID ngokusho kwemigomo esemthethweni.
Inani labafayo ngempela ngenxa ye-COVID-19 lingaba likhulu kakhulu, njengoba lingase lingafaki abantu abafa ngaphandle kokuhlolwa - isibonelo, ekhaya, emakhaya asebekhulile, njll.
Imininingwane eyingxenye evela e-Italy ithole ukuthi inani labantu abafe ngokweqile phakathi nalolu bhubhane lidlule inani elibhalwe ngokusemthethweni labantu abafe ngenxa ye-COVID ngokuphindwe izikhathi ezingu-4-5.
"Isikhulumi se-U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) savuma ukuthi ""Siyazi ukuthi [inani elichaziwe labafile] lilinganisiwe kancane"", isitatimende esiqinisekiswe imibiko yezenzakalo ezenzeka e-U.S. Ukubukelwa phansi okunjalo kuvame ukwenzeka ezifweni eziwumqedazwe, njengesifo sohlobo lwe-H1N1 sezingulube ngo-2009. Ukufa kokuqala okuqinisekisiwe kwaba eWuhan ngo-9 Januwari 2020. "
Ukufa kokuqala ngaphandle kweChina kwaqala ngoFebhuwari 1 ePhilippines, kanti ukufa kokuqala ngaphandle kwe-Asia kwaba eFrance ngoFebhuwari 14.
Ngo-February 28, ngaphandle kweChina, kwafa abantu abangaphezu kweshumi nambili e-Iran, eNingizimu Korea nase-Italy.
Ngo-March 13, amazwe angaphezu kwamashumi amane nezindawo zase zibike ukufa, kuwo wonke amazwekazi ngaphandle kwe-Antarctica. Izilinganiso eziningana zivame ukusetshenziselwa ukulinganisa inani labantu abafayo.
Lezi zibalo ziyahlukahluka kuye ngesifunda nangesikhathi, futhi zithonywa inani lokuhlolwa, ikhwalithi yohlelo lwezempilo, izindlela zokwelashwa, isikhathi selokhu kwaqubuka isifo, kanye nezici zomphakathi ezinjengobudala, ubulili, nempilo jikelele. Isilinganiso sokufa kuya esimweni sibonisa inani labafile elihlukaniswe ngenani lamacala atholakalayo esikhathini esithile.
Ngokusekelwe ezibalweni ze-Johns Hopkins University, isilinganiso sokufa kwabantu emhlabeni wonke singu-6.0% (97,039/1,617,204) kusukela ngomhlaka-10 Ephreli 2020.
Inani liyahlukahluka kuye ngezindawo.
EChina, izilinganiso zokushona kwabantu ezibhekene nezinkinga ze-HIV zehle zisuka ku-17.3% (kulabo abaqala ukuboniswa izimpawu ngo-1-10 Januwari 2020) zaya ku-0.7% (kulabo abaqala ukuboniswa izimpawu ngemuva kuka-1 kuFebhuwari 2020). Ezinye izilinganiso zifaka phakathi izinga lokufa kwabantu (CFR), elibonisa iphesenti labantu abatholakale ukuthi babulawa isifo, kanye nezinga lokufa kwabantu abathelelekile (IFR), elibonisa iphesenti labantu abathelelekile (abaxilongwe futhi abangatholakali) abafa ngenxa yesifo.
Lezi zibalo azibophekile ngesikhathi futhi zilandela inani elithile labantu kusukela ekuthelelekeni kuya ekuxazululeni amacala.
Izazi eziningi ziye zazama ukubala lezi zibalo zabantu abathile.
Isikhungo se-Oxford University's Centre for Evidence-Based Medicine silinganisela ukuthi izinga lokufa kwabantu ngenxa yalolu bhubhane lilonke liphakathi kuka-0,1% no-0,39%.
Isilinganiso esiphezulu salokhu kuhlukahluka siyavumelana nemiphumela yokuhlolwa kokuqala okungahleliwe kwe-COVID-19 eJalimane, kanye nesifundo sezibalo esihlaziya umthelela wokuhlolwa kwe-CFR.
I-WHO ithi lesi sifo esiwumshayabhuqe singalawulwa.
Isikhathi esiphezulu nesikhathi esiphelele sokuqubuka akuqinisekile futhi kungahluka kuye ngendawo.
"UMaciej Boni wasePenn State University wathi, "Uma kungalawulwa, ukuqubuka kwezifo ezithathelwanayo kuvame ukuba sezingeni eliphezulu bese kuqala ukwehla lapho lesi sifo siphela iziphathimandla ezitholakalayo".
"Kodwa cishe akunakwenzeka ukwenza noma yikuphi ukuqagela okunengqondo njengamanje mayelana nokuthi lokho kuyoba nini".
"Umeluleki omkhulu wezokwelapha kahulumeni waseChina uZhong Nanshan waphikisana ngokuthi ""kungase kuphele ngoJuni"" uma wonke amazwe engakwazi ukuhlanganiswa ukuze alandele iseluleko se-WHO ngezinyathelo zokuvimba ukusabalala kwegciwane".
"Ngo-Mashi 17, u-Adam Kucharski waseLondon School of Hygiene &amp; Tropical Medicine wathi i-SARS-CoV-2 ""izohlala ikhona, mhlawumbe unyaka noma emibili".
"Ngokusho kocwaningo lwe-Imperial College oluholwa nguNeil Ferguson, kuyodingeka ukuba umuntu ahlale kude nomunye umuntu nezinye izinyathelo "kuze kutholakale umuthi wokugoma (okungenzeka izinyanga ezingu-18 noma ngaphezulu) ".
"UWilliam Schaffner waseVanderbilt University wathi, ""Ngicabanga ukuthi akunakwenzeka ukuthi le coronavirus  ngoba idluliseka kalula  izonyamalala ngokuphelele"" futhi ""ingaphenduka ibe isifo sesizini, ibuye njalo ngonyaka". "
Ukubuya kwe-virus kuyoxhomeka emandleni omhlambi okuzivikela kanye nasebangeni lokuvela kwezinto eziguqukayo.
Izimpawu ze-COVID-19 zingaba ezingajwayelekile futhi abantu abangenayo kungenzeka bangabi nazo izimpawu.
Izimpawu ezimbili ezivame kakhulu ukushisa (88%) nokukhwehlela okomile (68%).
Izimpawu ezivamile zihlanganisa ukukhathala, ukukhiqizwa kwesicanucanu (i-phlegm), ukulahlekelwa umuzwa wokuhogela, ukuphefumula kanzima, ubuhlungu bemisipha namalunga, ubuhlungu bomphimbo, ikhanda, ukuqhaqhazela, ukuhlanza, ukuvuvukala kwegazi, isifo sohudo, noma i-cyanosis. I-WHO ithi cishe umuntu oyedwa kwabayisithupha uyagula kakhulu futhi unenkinga yokuphefumula.
Izikhungo Zase-U.S. Zokulawulwa Nokuvinjelwa Kwezifo (CDC) zibhala izimpawu eziphuthumayo njengobunzima bokuphefumula, ubuhlungu noma ingcindezi yesifuba eqhubekayo, ukudideka okungazelelwe, ubunzima bokuvuka, kanye nobuso noma izindebe ezibomvu; kunconywa ukunakekelwa kwezokwelapha ngokushesha uma lezi zimpawu zikhona. Ukuthuthuka okwengeziwe kwalesi sifo kungaholela emgodini omkhulu wamaphaphu, i-acute respiratory distress syndrome, i-sepsis, i-septic shock nokufa.
Abanye abantu abangenayo ingase ingabi khona imithelela, ingabi khona izimpawu kodwa ibe nemiphumela yokuhlolwa eqinisekisa ukuthi banayo, ngakho-ke abacwaningi baye banikeza iseluleko sokuthi labo abasondelene kakhulu nabantu abaqinisekisiwe ukuthi banayo kufanele babhekwe futhi bahlolwe ukuze kuvinjelwe ukutheleleka.
Izilinganiso zaseChina zokuthi kunabantu abambalwa abangabonisi zimpawu eziyingozi kuya kwabangu-44%.
Isikhathi esivamile sokukhulelwa (isikhathi esiphakathi kokutheleleka nokuqala kwezimpawu) sisukela ezinsukwini ezingu-1 kuya kwezingu-14; ngokuvamile kuba izinsuku ezinhlanu. Njengesibonelo sokungaqiniseki, ukulinganiselwa kwenani labantu abane-COVID-19 abalahlekelwa umuzwa wokuhogela ekuqaleni kwakungu-30% futhi kamuva kwehla kwaba ngu-15%.
Ezinye izinto eziphathelene nendlela lesi sifo esakazeka ngayo zisazotholakele.
Kukholakala ukuthi lesi sifo sisakazeka ngokuyinhloko lapho umuntu ehlangana eduze naye futhi ngamaconsi amancane akhiqizwa lapho ekhwehlela, ethimula noma ekhuluma; lapho umuntu ehlangana eduze kungakapheli amamitha angu-1 kuya kwangu-2 (3 kuya ku-6 feet).
Ucwaningo luye lwathola ukuthi ukukhwehlela ngaphandle kokumboza kungaholela ekutheni kube namathontsi ahamba amamitha angu-4,5 kuya kwangu-8,2 (amamitha angu-27).
Abanye baye basikisela ukuthi leli gciwane lingadluliselwa ngamathontsi amancane ahlala isikhathi eside emoyeni, angakhishwa lapho kukhulunywa. Amathontsi okuphefumula nawo angakhiqizwa lapho kuphuma umoya, kuhlanganise nalapho kukhulunywa, nakuba ngokuvamile leli gciwane lingadluliselwa emoyeni.
La mathonsi angahlala emlonyeni noma emakhaleni abantu abaseduze noma angahle afakwe emaphashini.
Ezinye izinqubo zokwelapha ezinjengokufakwa komjovo wokungenisa umoya nokuvuselelwa kwenhliziyo (i-CPR) zingase zenze ukuba imifudlana ephefumula ihlukaniswe umoya futhi ngaleyo ndlela ihlukaniswe nomoya.
Ingase isakazeke nalapho umuntu ethinta indawo engcolisiwe, kuhlanganise nesikhumba, bese ethinta amehlo, ikhala noma umlomo.
Nakuba kunokukhathazeka ngokuthi ingase isakazeke ngezicucu, lokhu kucatshangwa ukuthi kuyingozi encane.
Uhulumeni waseChina waphika ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 idluliselwe ngezindlebe. Leli gciwane lidlulela kakhulu ezinsukwini ezintathu zokuqala ngemva kokuqala kwezimpawu, nakuba ukusakazeka kungenzeka ngaphambi kokuba izimpawu zivele nasezigabeni zakamuva zesifo.
Abantu baye bahlolwa ukuthi banesifo kuze kube yizinsuku ezintathu ngaphambi kokuqala kwezimpawu okusikisela ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi basidlulisele ngaphambi kokuba baveze izimpawu eziphawulekayo.
Kunemibiko embalwa kuphela yamacala angenayo izimpawu eqinisekiswe ngelebhu, kodwa ukusabalala okungenayo izimpawu kuye kwabonwa kwamanye amazwe phakathi nophenyo lokulandelela abantu abaxhumana nabo.
I-European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control (ECDC) ithi nakuba kungacaci kahle ukuthi lesi sifo sisakazeka kalula kangakanani, umuntu oyedwa uvame ukuthelela abanye ababili kuya kwabathathu. Igciwane lihlala amahora noma izinsuku ezindaweni.
Ngokuqondile, kwatholakala ukuthi leli gciwane litholakala izinsuku ezintathu epulasitiki (i-polypropylene) nensimbi engagqwali engu-304, usuku olulodwa ekhadibhodi, futhi amahora amane etholakala ethusi.
Nokho, lokhu kuyehluka kuye ngomswakama nangokushisa. Izilwane ezifuywayo nezinye izilwane ziye zahlolwa zathola i-COVID-19.
Abukho ubufakazi bokuthi izilwane zingadlulisela leli gciwane kubantu, nakuba iziphathimandla zaseBrithani zeluleka ukuba umuntu ageze izandla ngemva kokuthintana nezilwane, njengokuthintana nezinye izindawo abantu abangenwe yilesi sifo abangase bazithinte.
I-severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (i-SARS-CoV-2) yigciwane elisha, elaqala ukuhlukaniswa kubantu abathathu abanesifo samaphaphu esihlobene neqembu lezimo ezibucayi zokuphefumula eWuhan.
Zonke izici zenoveli SARS-CoV-2 zenzeka kuma-coronavirus ahlobene emvelweni. Ngaphandle komzimba womuntu, leli gciwane libulawa ngensipho yasendlini, eyenza ukuthi umgoqo walo wokuvikela uchitheke. I-SARS-CoV-2 ihlobene kakhulu ne-SARS-CoV yokuqala.
Kucatshangwa ukuthi ivela ezihlahleni.
Ukuhlaziywa kofuzo kuveze ukuthi i-coronavirus ihlangana nohlobo lwe-Betacoronavirus, ku-subgenus Sarbecovirus (igama B) kanye nezinhlobo ezimbili ezivela emathangeni.
Ifana ngo-96% ezingeni le-genome yonke namanye amasampula e-bat coronavirus (i-BatCov RaTG13).
Ngo-February 2020, abacwaningi baseChina bathola ukuthi kunomehluko owodwa kuphela kuma-amino acid ezingxenyeni ezithile zamasekhondi e-genome phakathi kwamagciwane avela kuma-pangolin nalawo avela kubantu.
Ukuqhathaniswa kwe-genome yonke kuze kube manje kuthole okungenani u-92% wezakhi zofuzo ezihlanganiswe phakathi kwe-pangolin coronavirus ne-SARS-CoV-2, okunganele ukufakazela ukuthi ama-pangolin angumninikhaya ophakathi.
Ukutheleleka ngegciwane kungahlolwa okwesikhashana ngesisekelo sezimpawu, nakuba ekugcineni kuqinisekiswa ngokudluliselwa kwe-polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) kwemithombo enegciwane noma nge-CT imaging.
Ucwaningo olwaqhathanisa i-PCR ne-CT eWuhan luye lwabonisa ukuthi i-CT izwela kakhulu kune-PCR, nakuba ingacacanga kangako, futhi izici zayo eziningi zokuthwebula izithombe zihlale zihambisana nezinye izifo zomoya kanye nezinqubo zezifo.
"Ngo-Mashi 2020, i-American College of Radiology incoma ukuthi ""i-CT akufanele isetshenziselwe ukuhlola noma njengokuhlolwa kokuqala kokuthola i-COVID-19".
I-WHO ishicilele ama-protocol amaningi okuhlola i-RNA ye-SARS-CoV-2, eyokuqala eyakhishwa ngo-January 17.
