I-pneumonia, i-ARI eyinhloko, iyimbangela eyinhloko yokufa kwezingane ezingaphansi kweminyaka emihlanu ubudala, ebulala izingane ezingaba izigidi ezingu - 1,8 ngonyaka.
Ukuhlanza kanye ne - pneumonia kubulala izingane ezingaba izigidi ezingu - 3,5 minyaka yonke.
Ngokwe-UNICEF, ukugeza izandla ngensipho ngaphambi kokudla nangemva kokusebenzisa indlu yangasese kuwumkhuba osungulwe ngokuqinile ongasindisa ukuphila kwabantu abaningi kunanoma imuphi umuthi wokugoma noma ukungenelela kwezokwelapha, kunciphise ukufa kwabantu ababulawa isifo sohudo cishe ngesigamu futhi kunciphise ukufa kwabantu ababulawa izifo eziyingozi zokuphefumula ngengxenye eyodwa kwezine.
Ukugeza izandla kuvame ukuhlanganiswa nezinye izinyathelo zokuhlanzeka njengengxenye yezinhlelo zamanzi, ukuhlanzeka kanye nenhlanzeko (WASH).
Ukugeza izandla kuvikela nasekuguleni okudluliselwa ngokuxhumana nomzimba.
Umphumela omncane omubi wokugeza izandla ukuthi ukugeza izandla kaningi kungaholela ekulimaleni kwesikhumba ngenxa yokoma kwesikhumba.
Ucwaningo olwenziwa eDenmark ngo-2012 lwathola ukuthi ukugeza izandla ngokweqile kungabangela isikhumba esibuhlungu esibizwa ngokuthi i-eczema noma i-dermatitis, okuyinto evame kakhulu phakathi kwabasebenzi bezempilo.
Ukugeza izandla njalo kakhulu nakho kubhekwa njengenye yezimpawu zokuphazamiseka okucindezelayo.
Kunezikhathi ezinhlanu ezibalulekile phakathi nosuku lapho ukugeza izandla ngensipho kubalulekile khona ukunciphisa ukudluliselwa kwezifo ngomlomo: ngemva kokusebenzisa indlu yangasese (ukuhlanza, ukuhlanza), ngemva kokuhlanza ingane (ukushintsha amapeyi), ngaphambi kokondla ingane, ngaphambi kokudla nangaphambi/emva kokulungisa ukudla noma ukuphatha inyama eluhlaza, inhlanzi noma izinkukhu.
Ezinye izikhathi lapho kufanele kwenziwe khona indlela efanele yokugeza izandla ukuze kuvinjelwe ukutheleleka kwezifo zihlanganisa ngaphambi nangemva kokwelapha isilonda; ngemva kokuthunta, ukukhwehlela, noma ukuphupha; ngemva kokuthinta indle yezilwane noma ukuphatha izilwane; nangemva kokuthinta udoti.
Emazweni amaningi, inani labantu abageza izandla ngensipho lincane.
Ucwaningo lokuhlanza izandla emazweni angama-54 ngo-2015 luthole ukuthi ngokwesilinganiso, ama-38.7% emakhaya ayegeza izandla ngensipho. Ucwaningo lwango-2014 lwabonisa ukuthi iSaudi Arabia yayinezinga eliphakeme kakhulu elingamaphesenti angu-97; i-United States yayiseduze naphakathi ngamaphesenti angu-77; neChina yayinezinga eliphansi kakhulu elingamaphesenti angu-23. Manje sekukhona izindlela eziningana zokushintsha indlela yokuziphatha ukuze kwandiswe ukujwayela ukuziphatha kokugeza izandla ngensipho ngezikhathi ezibucayi. Ukugeza izandla kweqembu kwezingane zesikole ngezikhathi ezithile zosuku kuyindlela emazweni asathuthuka yokugxilisa ukugeza izandla ekuziphatheni kwezingane.
"I-"Essential Health Care Program" esetshenziswa uMnyango Wezemfundo ePhilippines iyisibonelo sokusebenza ngezinga elikhulu ukuze kuthuthukiswe impilo nemfundo yezingane".
Ukuhlanza izimpethu kabili ngonyaka, okuhambisana nokuwasha izandla nsuku zonke ngensipho, ukuxubha amazinyo nsuku zonke nge-fluoride, kuyisici esiyinhloko sale nhlelo kazwelonke.
Iphinde yasetshenziswa ngempumelelo e-Indonesia.
Ukususwa kwezinambuzane esikhumbeni kuthuthukiswa ngokungezwa kwamanzi ngensipho noma ngemithi yokuwasha.
Umsebenzi oyinhloko wamasobho nezithako zokuwasha ukunciphisa izithiyo ezivimbela ukuncibilikisa, nokwandisa ukuncibilika.
Amanzi wodwa awasihlanzi kahle isikhumba ngoba amafutha namaprotheni, ayingxenye yomhlabathi, awaxazululeki kalula emanzini.
Nokho, ukuhlanzwa kuyasizwa ukugeleza kwamanzi okunengqondo.
Ngenxa yokuthi insipho eqinile ingaphinda isetshenziswe, ingaqukatha amagciwane atholakala ekusetshenzisweni kwayo ngaphambili.
Inani elincane lezifundo eziye zahlola ukudluliselwa kwamagciwane esaphuzini esinobala elingcolisiwe ziye zaphetha ngokuthi ukudluliselwa kwamagciwane akunakwenzeka njengoba amagciwane egeza nge-foam.
"I-CDC isasho ukuthi ""isabha esinemikhono engenamikhono iyathandeka""."
Amasabha alwa namagciwane aye akhuthazwa kakhulu emphakathini owaziyo ukuthi unempilo.
Kuze kube manje, abukho ubufakazi bokuthi ukusebenzisa ama - antiseptic noma izibulala - magciwane okuphakanyisiwe kuyayivikela imithi elwa namagciwane emvelweni.
Nokho, amasabha alwa namagciwane aqukethe ama-antibacterial agents ajwayelekile njenge-triclosan, enezinhlobo eziningi zezinto eziphilayo eziphikisayo.
Ngakho, ngisho noma izinhlobo eziphikisana nemithi elwa namagciwane zingakhethwa ngamasobho alwa namagciwane, zingase zingabi nethonya njengoba zithengiswa.
Ngaphandle kwe-surfactant ne-agent evikela isikhumba, ama-formulations ayinkimbinkimbi angase aqukethe ama-acid (acetic acid, ascorbic acid, lactic acid) njengombusi we-pH, i-benzoic acid esebenza ngokumelene namagciwane kanye nezinye izinto eziqinisa isikhumba (i-aloe vera, amavithamini, i-menthol, izithako zezitshalo). Ukuhlaziywa okuphelele okuvela e-University of Oregon School of Public Health kwabonisa ukuthi amasabha avamile ayasebenza njengamasabha avamile okuvikela amagciwane aqukethe i-triclosan ekuvimbeleni izifo nasekususeni amagciwane ezandleni.
Amanzi ashisayo akulungele ukugeza izandla awashisi ngokwanele ukuba abulale amagciwane.
Amagciwane akhula ngokushesha okukhulu ekushiseni komzimba (37 ¬∞C).
Nokho, amanzi afudumele anensipho asebenza kangcono kunamanzi abandayo anensipho ekususeni amafutha emvelo agcina inhlabathi namagciwane.
Nokho, ngokuphambene nalokho okucatshangwa abaningi, ucwaningo lwesayensi luye lwabonisa ukuthi ukusebenzisa amanzi afudumele akunamthelela ekunciphiseni umthwalo wamagciwane ezandleni.
I-hand sanitizer noma i-antiseptic yezandla iyindlela yokuhlanza izandla engasekelwe emanzini.
Ngasekupheleni kwawo-1990 nasekuqaleni kwekhulu lama-21, izinto zokuhlanzeka zezandla ezingasuselwa emanzini ezaziwa nangokuthi ama-hand rubs asekelwe otshwaleni, ama-antiseptic hand rubs, noma ama-hand sanitizers zaqala ukuthandwa.
Iningi lisuselwa ku-isopropyl alcohol noma i-ethanol eyenziwe kanye ne- thickening agent efana ne-Carbomer (polymer ye-acrylic acid) ibe yi-gel, noma i-humicant efana ne-glycerin ibe yi-liquid, noma i-foam ukuze kube lula ukuyisebenzisa futhi kunciphise umphumela wokomisa wotshwala.
Ukungeza i-hydrogen-peroxide encibilikisiwe kwandisa umsebenzi wokulwa namagciwane. Ama-sanitizer ezandla aqukethe okungenani u-60-95% wotshwala ayingozi ekubulaleni amagciwane.
Izidakamizwa zokuhlanza ngotshwala zibulala amagciwane, amagciwane amelana nemithi eminingi (i-MRSA ne-VRE), isifo sofuba, namanye amagciwane (kuhlanganise ne-HIV, i-herpes, i-RSV, i-rhinovirus, i-vaccinia, umkhuhlane, ne-hepatitis) namafungus.
Ama-sanitizer anotshwala aqukethe u-70% wotshwala abulala ama-bacterium ezandleni angu-99.97% (ukunciphisa okungu-3.5 log, okufana nokunciphisa okungu-35 decibel) ngemva kwemizuzwana engu-30 esebenzile futhi abulala ama-bacterium ezandleni angu-99.99% kuya ku-99.999% (ukunciphisa okungu-4 kuya ku-5 log) ngemva komzuzu owodwa esebenzile. Ama-sanitizer ezandla asebenza kakhulu ekulweni namagciwane futhi awabi nethonya elinamandla ekulweni namanye amagciwane.
Izidakamizwa zokuhlanza izandla ezinotshwala azisebenzi ngokuphelele ngokumelene namagciwane ohlobo lwe-norovirus (noma i-Norwalk), okuyimbangela evame kakhulu yokutheleleka komzimba. Kufanele kusetshenziswe i-antiseptic eyanele noma utshwala ukuze kufakwe amanzi kahle noma amboze izandla zombili.
Ingxenye engaphambili nangemuva kwezandla zombili, phakathi nezinhlangothi zeminwe yonke kuyasuswa cishe imizuzwana engu-30 kuze kube yilapho uketshezi, i-foam noma i-gel isomile.
Izindololwane zeminwe nazo kufanele zigezwe kahle, zifuthwe ezandleni zombili. I-US Center for Disease Control and Prevention incoma ukugeza izandla phezu kwe-sanitizer yezandla, ikakhulukazi uma izandla zingcolile.
Ukusetshenziswa okwandayo kwalezi zinsiza kusekelwe ekusebenziseni kwazo kalula nasekusebenzeni kwazo ngokushesha ekubulaleni amagciwane; noma kunjalo, akufanele zisebenze njengendawo yokuhlanza izandla ngendlela efanele ngaphandle uma amanzi nensipho kungatholakali.
Ukusetshenziswa kaningi kwama-hand sanitizer anotshwala kungabangela isikhumba esomile ngaphandle uma kufakwa ama-emollients kanye/noma ama-moisturizers esikhumba.
Umphumela wokomisa utshwala ungancishiswa noma ususwe ngokungezwa kwe-glycerin kanye/noma ezinye izinto ezithambisa umzimba.
Ekuvivinyweni kwemitholampilo, izihlanzi zezandla ezenziwe ngotshwala eziqukethe ama-emollients zabangela ukucasuka nokoma kwesikhumba okuncane kakhulu kunamasepha noma izidakamizwa zokuhlanza ezilwa namagciwane.
I-allergic contact dermatitis, i-urticaria syndrome noma ukuzwela ngokweqile utshwala noma izithasiselo ezikhona ekubhuzeni izandla ngotshwala akuvamile ukuba khona.
Ukuthambekela okuncane kokubangela i-dermatitis yokuxhumana ecasulayo kwaba yinto ekhangayo uma kuqhathaniswa nokugeza izandla ngensipho namanzi.
Naphezu kokusebenza kwawo, izinto ezingezona amanzi azihlanzi izandla ngezinto eziphilayo, kodwa zimane nje zizibulala amagciwane.
Yingakho ama - hand sanitizer engase abe ngempumelelo njengamanzi nensipho ekuvimbeleni ukusakazeka kwamagciwane amaningi, njengoba amagciwane esekhona ezandleni.
Ukusebenza kahle kwesicoci sezandla esingenalo utshwala kuncike kakhulu ezintweni ezisetshenziswayo nasekwakhiweni kwaso, futhi ngokomlando sinomsebenzi omncane kakhulu kunotshwala kanye nokugcoba utshwala.
Muva nje, kuye kwaboniswa ukuthi ama - formulations asebenzisa i - benzalkonium chloride anokusebenza okuqhubekayo nokwakhayo kwe - antimicrobial ngemva kokusetshenziswa, ngokungafani notshwala, okuye kwaboniswa ukuthi buyancipha ngemva kokusetshenziswa ngokuphindaphindiwe, cishe ngenxa yokwanda kwemiphumela emibi yesikhumba.
Abantu abaningi emiphakathini engenayo imali eningi abakwazi ukuthenga insipho bese besebenzisa umlotha noma inhlabathi esikhundleni salokho.
Umlotha noma inhlabathi kungase kube nethonya elikhulu kunamanzi kuphela, kodwa kungase kube nethonya elincane kunesepha.
Esinye isizathu sokukhathazeka ukuthi uma inhlabathi noma umlotha ungcoliswe izinambuzane, kungase kwenze izifo zisabalale kakhulu kunokuba zinciphe.
Njenge - sabhu, umlotha nawo uyindlela yokubulala amagciwane ngoba lapho uthintana namanzi, wakha isixazululo esinamafutha.
I-WHO yancoma umlotha noma isihlabathi njengenye indlela yokusebenzisa insipho lapho insipho ingekho.
