Ukuze kulawulwe izifo ze-staphylococcal ezibhedlela, kwatholakala ukuthi inzuzo enkulu kakhulu yokuhlanza izandla yayivela kuma-20% okuqala okugeza, futhi inzuzo eyengeziwe yayincane kakhulu lapho ukuhlanza izandla kwanda ngaphezu kwama-35%.
Ukugeza ngensipho elula kuholela ekutheni kube nezifo ezithathelwanayo ezibangelwa amagciwane ezidluliselwa ekudleni ezingaphezu kokuphindwe kathathu uma kuqhathaniswa nokuwasha ngensipho elwa namagciwane. Ukuqhathanisa ukugeza izandla ngesisombululo esisekelwe otshwaleni nokuwasha izandla ngensipho elwa namagciwane isikhathi esiphakathi semizuzwana engu-30 ngakunye kwabonisa ukuthi ukugeza izandla ngensipho elwa namagciwane kunciphise ukungcoliswa kwamagciwane ngo-26%, kunokusebenzisa insipho elwa namagciwane.
Kodwa insipho namanzi kuyasebenza kakhulu kunama-rubs asezandleni anotshwala ekunciphiseni igciwane le-H1N1 influenza A kanye nama-spore e-Clostridium difficile ezandleni. Ukungenelela okuthuthukisa inhlanzeko yezandla ezindaweni zokunakekelwa kwezempilo kungahlanganisa ukufundisa abasebenzi ngokuhlanza izandla, ukwandisa ukutholakala kwama-rubs asezandleni anotshwala, kanye nezikhumbuzo ezibhaliwe nezomlomo kubasebenzi.
Kudingeka ucwaningo olwengeziwe mayelana nokuthi yikuphi kwalokhu kungenelela okuphumelela kakhulu ezimweni ezihlukahlukene zokunakekelwa kwezempilo.
Emazweni asathuthuka, ukugeza izandla ngensipho kuyaqashelwa njengethuluzi elingenayo imali, elibalulekile lokufeza impilo enhle, ngisho nokudla okunempilo.
Nokho, ukuntuleka kwamanzi athembekile, insipho noma izindawo zokuwasha izandla emakhaya abantu, ezikoleni nasendaweni yokusebenzela kwenza kube inselele ukufinyelela ukuziphatha okuvamile kokugeza izandla.
Ngokwesibonelo, emaphandleni amaningi ase-Afrika, amaphampu okugeza izandla asemancane eduze kwawo wonke amathilomu angawomuntu siqu noma omphakathi, nakuba kunezindlela ezishibhile zokwakha iziteshi zokuwasha izandla.
Nokho, izinga eliphansi lokuwasha izandla lingaba umphumela wemikhuba egxilile kunokuba kube ngenxa yokuntuleka kwensipho noma amanzi.
Ukukhuthazwa nokukhuthazwa kokugeza izandla ngensipho kungathonya izinqumo zenqubomgomo, kukhulise ukuqwashisa ngezinzuzo zokugeza izandla futhi kuholele ekushintsheni kokuziphatha kwabantu esikhathini eside.
Ukuze lokhu kusebenze kahle, kudingeka ukuqapha nokuhlola.
"Ukubuyekezwa okuhlelekile kwezifundo ezingu-70 kuthole ukuthi izindlela ezisuselwa emphakathini ziyasebenza ekwandiseni ukugeza izandla kuma-LMIC, kuyilapho imikhankaso yokumaketha kwezenhlalo ingasebenzi kangako. Esinye isibonelo sokukhuthaza ukugeza izandla ezikoleni yi-"Three Star Approach" ye-UNICEF ekhuthaza izikole ukuba zithathe izinyathelo ezilula, ezingabizi ukuqinisekisa ukuthi abafundi bahlanza izandla zabo ngensipho, phakathi kwezinye izidingo zenhlanzeko. "
Lapho kufinyelelwa izindinganiso ezincane, izikole zingashintsha zisuke enkanyezini eyodwa ziye kwezintathu.
Ukwakha iziteshi zokuwasha izandla kungaba ingxenye yemikhankaso yokukhuthaza ukuwasha izandla eyenziwa ukuze kuncishiswe izifo nokufa kwezingane.
Usuku Lokuwasha Izandla Emhlabeni Wonke lungesinye isibonelo somkhankaso wokuqwashisa ozama ukufeza ushintsho ekuziphatheni. Ngenxa yobhadane lwe-coronavirus lwango-2019/20, i-UNICEF yakhuthaza ukusetshenziswa kwe-emoji yokuwasha izandla.
Izifundo ezimbalwa ziye zacabangela izindleko eziphelele zokuwasha izandla emazweni asathuthuka ngokuphathelene nama-DALY agwenywe.
Nokho, ukubuyekezwa okuthile kusikisela ukuthi ukukhuthaza ukugeza izandla ngensipho kunenzuzo kakhulu kunezinye izindlela zokuphuza amanzi nezokuhlanza.
"Ukubaluleka kokugeza izandla empilweni yabantu  ikakhulukazi kubantu abasesimweni esibucayi njengabomama abasanda kuzala noma amasosha alimele ezibhedlela  kwaqala ukubonwa maphakathi nekhulu le-19 ngamaphayona amabili okuhlanzeka kwezandla: udokotela waseHungary u-Ignaz Semmelweis owayesebenza eVienna, e-Austria noFlorence Nightingale, "umsunguli wezokwelapha kwanamuhla" waseNgilandi".
Ngaleso sikhathi abantu abaningi babesakholelwa ukuthi izifo zabangelwa iphunga elibi elibizwa ngokuthi i-miasmas.
Ngawo-1980, ukuqubuka kokudla nezifo ezihlobene nokunakekelwa kwezempilo kwaholela e-United States Centers for Disease Control and Prevention ukuba ikhuthaze ngenkuthalo inhlanzeko yezandla njengendlela ebalulekile yokuvimbela ukusabalala kokutheleleka.
Ukuqubuka komkhuhlane wezingulube ngo-2009 kanye nobhadane lwe-COVID-19 ngo-2020 kwaholela ekwandeni kokuqwashisa emazweni amaningi ngokubaluleka kokugeza izandla ngensipho ukuze umuntu azivikele ezifweni ezinjalo ezithathelwanayo.
"Ngokwesibonelo, amaposta anendlela "elungile yokuwasha izandla" ayephanyekwe eduze kwezindawo zokugeza izandla emathilomu omphakathi nasemathilomu ezakhiwo zamahhovisi nasezikhumulweni zezindiza eJalimane".
"Igama elithi "ukugeza izandla" lisho ukuthi umuntu akafuni ukuthatha umthwalo wemfanelo walokho noma ukuhlanganyela kukho".
Ivela esigabeni seBhayibheli kuMathewu lapho uPontiyu Pilatu egeza izandla zakhe esinqumweni sokubethela uJesu Kristu, kodwa sekuyinkulumo esetshenziswa kabanzi kakhulu kwezinye izindawo zesiNgisi.
KuMacbeth kaShakespeare, uLady Macbeth uqala ukugeza izandla zakhe ngenkani ezama ukuhlanza ibala elicatshangelwe, elimelela unembeza wakhe onecala mayelana nobugebengu abubonile futhi wabangela umyeni wakhe ukuba abubophe.
Kuye kwatholakala nokuthi abantu, ngemva kokukhumbula noma ukucabanga ngezenzo ezingekho emthethweni, bathambekele ekugezeni izandla kaningi kunabanye, futhi bathambekele ekuhlonipheni kakhulu imishini yokuwasha izandla.
"Ngaphezu kwalokho, labo abavunyelwe ukugeza izandla zabo ngemva kokubheka izinto ezinjalo mancane amathuba okuba bahlanganyele kwezinye izenzo zokuzihlanza, njengokuzithandela".
