Ukulawulwa kwezingozi emsebenzini ze-COVID-19
Ukulawulwa kwezingozi emsebenzini ngenxa ye-COVID-19 ukusetshenziswa kwezindlela zokuphepha kwezempilo emsebenzini ukuze kulawulwe izingozi zokuvimbela isifo i-coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Ukulawulwa kwezingozi okufanele emsebenzini kuxhomeke endaweni yokusebenzela nasemsebenzini, okusekelwe ekuhlolweni kwengozi yemithombo yokuchayeka, ubukhulu besifo emphakathini kanye nezici zobungozi zabasebenzi ngabanye abangase babe sengozini yokuthola i-COVID-19.
Ngokwe-U.S. Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA), imisebenzi enobungozi obuncane inokuxhumana okuncane nomphakathi nabanye osebenza nabo, okuphakanyiswayo ukuthi bathathe izinyathelo eziyisisekelo zokuvimbela ukutheleleka, ezihlanganisa ukugeza izandla, ukukhuthaza abasebenzi ukuba bahlale ekhaya uma begula, isimilo sokuphefumula, nokugcina ukuhlanza nokubulala amagciwane okuvamile kwendawo yokusebenza.
Imisebenzi enobungozi obuphakathi ifaka phakathi leyo edinga ukuxhumana njalo noma eduze nabantu abangaziwa noma abasolwa ukuthi bane-COVID-19, kodwa abangase babe negciwane ngenxa yokudluliselwa komphakathi okuqhubekayo noma ukuhamba kwamanye amazwe.
Lokhu kuhlanganisa abasebenzi abaxhumana nomphakathi jikelele njengas ezikoleni, ezindaweni zokusebenza ezinabantu abaningi, nakwezinye izindawo zokuthengisa ezinabantu abaningi.
Ukulawula ubungozi baleli qembu, ngaphezu kwezinyathelo eziyisisekelo zokuvimbela ukutheleleka, kuhlanganisa ukuphefumula kusetshenziswa izihlungi zomoya ezisebenza kahle, izivikelo zokuthimula, nokuba nemishini yokuzivikela uma umuntu ene-COVID-19 etholakala.
I-OSHA ibheka abasebenzi bezempilo nabasebenza emathunjini okuhlinza abavezwe umuntu owaziwayo noma osolwayo ukuthi une-COVID-19 njengosengozini enkulu yokuvezwa, okwandisa ingozi enkulu kakhulu uma abasebenzi benza izinqubo zokukhiqiza i-aerosol, noma beqoqa noma bephatha amasampula avela kumuntu owaziwayo noma osolwayo nge-COVID-19.
Ukulawula izingozi ezifanele zalaba basebenzi kuhlanganisa ukulawula ubunjiniyela njengamakamelo okuphefumulela umoya ngaphansi kwengcindezi engathandeki, nemishini yokuzivikela efanele umsebenzi.
Ukuqubuka kwe-COVID-19 kungaba nemiphumela eminingi emsebenzini.
Izisebenzi zingase zingabi khona emsebenzini ngenxa yokugula, ngenxa yesidingo sokunakekela abanye, noma ngenxa yokwesaba ukuchayeka okungenzeka.
Izindlela zokuhweba zingashintsha, kokubili ngokuphathelene nokuthi yiziphi izimpahla ezifunwayo, nezindlela zokuthola lezi zimpahla (njengokuthenga ngezikhathi ezingaphandle kwezikhathi eziphezulu noma ngokusebenzisa izinsizakalo zokulethwa noma zokushayela).
Okokugcina, ukuthunyelwa kwezinto ezivela ezindaweni ezihlushwa kakhulu yi-COVID-19 kungase kuphazamiseke. Uhlelo lokulungela nokusabela ezifweni ezithathelwanayo lungasetshenziswa ukuqondisa izenzo zokuzivikela.
Izinhlelo zibheka izinga lobungozi elihlobene nezindawo ezihlukahlukene zokusebenza nemisebenzi yomsebenzi, kuhlanganise nemithombo yokuchayeka, izimbangela zobungozi ezivela ekhaya nasemphakathini, kanye nezimbangela zobungozi zabasebenzi ngabanye njengobudala noma izimo zempilo ezingamahlalakhona.
Zibeka nemingcele yokulawula okudingekayo ukuze kubhekwane nalezo zingozi, namasu okubhekana nezimo ezingase zivele ngenxa yokuqubuka kwezifo.
Amasu okulungela nokusabela ezifweni ezithathelwanayo angase abe ngaphansi kwezincomo zikazwelonke noma ezingaphansi kukazwelonke.
Izinhloso zokuphendula ekuqubukeni zifaka ukunciphisa ukudluliselwa phakathi kwabasebenzi, ukuvikela abantu abasengozini enkulu yezinkinga zempilo, ukugcina imisebenzi yebhizinisi, nokunciphisa imiphumela emibi kwezinye izinhlangano ezisezintweni zabo zokuphakela.
Ubunzima besifo emphakathini lapho ibhizinisi likhona bunomthelela ekuphenduleni okuthathwayo.
I-hierarchy yokulawula izingozi iyisikhungo esisetshenziswa kabanzi ekuphepheni nasempilweni emsebenzini ukuhlela ukulawula izingozi ngokusebenza kahle.
Lapho izingozi ze-COVID-19 zingenakuqedwa khona, izindlela zokulawula eziphumelela kakhulu ukulawula ubunjiniyela, kulandelwe ukulawula kokuphatha, futhi ekugcineni imishini yokuzivikela.
Ukulawula ubunjiniyela kuhilela ukuhlukanisa abasebenzi ezingozini ezihlobene nomsebenzi ngaphandle kokuncika ekuziphatheni kwabasebenzi, futhi kungaba yisixazululo esisebenza kahle kakhulu sokusebenzisa.
Ukulawula okuphathelene nomsebenzi yizinguquko ezenzweni noma ezimisweni zomsebenzi ezidinga ukuba umsebenzi noma umqashi athathe isinyathelo.
Imishini yokuzivikela (PPE) ibhekwa njengengasebenzi kahle kunokuhlolwa kwezobunjiniyela nokwengamele, kodwa ingasiza ekuvimbeleni ukuchayeka okuthile.
Zonke izinhlobo ze-PPE kufanele zikhethwe ngokususelwa engozini ezisebenzela abasebenzi, zifakwe kahle uma kufanele (isb., imishini yokuphefumula), zigqoke njalo futhi ngendlela efanele, zihlolwe njalo, zigcinwe futhi zishintshwe, uma kunesidingo, futhi zisuswe ngendlela efanele, zihlanzwe, zigcinwe noma zilahlwe ukuze kugwenywe ukungcoliswa.
Ngokwe-U.S. Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA), imisebenzi enobungozi obuncane yokutholakala kwemithi enobuthi inokuxhumana okuncane nomphakathi nabanye osebenza nabo.
Izinyathelo eziyisisekelo zokuvimbela ukutheleleka ezinconyelwa zonke izindawo zokusebenza zihlanganisa ukugeza izandla njalo nangokuningiliziwe, ukukhuthaza abasebenzi ukuba bahlale ekhaya uma begula, isimilo sokuphefumula kuhlanganise nokumboza ukukhwehlela nokuthimula, ukuhlinzeka ngamathawula kanye nemithombo yokulahla udoti, ukulungiselela ukuhamba ngezindlela ezikude noma ukushintshana ngezikhathi uma kudingeka, ukugwema abasebenzi ekusebenziseni amathuluzi nemishini yabanye, nokugcina ukuhlanza nokubulala amagciwane okuvamile kwendawo yokusebenza.
Ukuhlonza ngokushesha nokuhlukanisa abantu abangase babe negciwane kuyisinyathelo esibalulekile ekuvikeleni abasebenzi, amakhasimende, izivakashi, nabanye abasendaweni yokusebenzela.
I-U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) incoma ukuthi abasebenzi abanezimpawu zesifo esibucayi sokuphefumula bahlale ekhaya kuze kube yilapho bengasenayo imfiva, izimpawu zomkhuhlane, nanoma iziphi ezinye izimpawu okungenani amahora angu-24 ngaphandle kokusebenzisa imithi yokunciphisa umkhuhlane noma eminye imithi eguqula izimpawu, nokuthi izinqubomgomo zokugula ziguquguqukayo, zivumela abasebenzi ukuba bahlale ekhaya ukuze banakekele ilungu lomkhaya eligulayo, nokuthi abasebenzi bayazi ngalezi zinqubomgomo.
Ngokusho kwe-OSHA, imisebenzi enobungozi obuphakathi ifaka phakathi leyo edinga ukuxhumana njalo noma eduze ngaphakathi kwamamitha ayisithupha (1.8 m) nabantu abangaziwa noma abasolwa ukuthi banesifo se-COVID-19, kodwa abangase babe ne-SARS-CoV-2 ngenxa yokudluliselwa komphakathi okuqhubekayo endaweni yebhizinisi, noma ngoba umuntu usanda kuhambela amazwe omhlaba endaweni yokudluliswa kwe-COVID-19.
Lokhu kufaka phakathi abasebenzi abaxhumana nomphakathi jikelele njengas ezikoleni, ezindaweni ezinabantu abaningi, kanye nezindawo ezithile zokuthengisa ezinabantu abaningi.Ulawulo lobunjiniyela lwalesi kanye namaqembu asezingeni eliphakeme lobungozi lubandakanya ukufakwa kwezihlungi zomoya ezisebenza kahle kakhulu, ukwanda kwamanani okuhamba komoya, ukufakwa kwezithiyo zomzimba ezinjengama-sniff guard e-plastic ecacile, nokufakwa kwefasitela lokuhamba ngamakhasimende.Ulawulo lwezokuphatha lwalesi kanye namaqembu asezingeni eliphakeme lobungozi lubandakanya ukukhuthaza abasebenzi abagulayo ukuthi bahlale ekhaya, ukufaka esikhundleni semihlangano ebonakalayo ngokuxhumana okubonakalayo, ukusungula amashifu ahlukanisiwe, ukuyeka ukuhamba okungabalulekile ezindaweni ezinokuqubuka kwe-COVID-19, ukuthuthukisa izinhlelo zokuxhumana kubandakanya iforamu yokuphendula izikhalo zabasebenzi, ukuhlinzeka ngemfundo yesimanje nokuqeqeshwa mayelana nezingozi ze-COVID-19 kanye nokuziphatha kwabasebenzi, ukuqeqesha abasebenzi ukuthi bangasebenzisa kanjani izingubo zokuzivikela, ukuhlinzeka ngemishini yokuvikela ubuso nokuhlanzeka, ukubeka izimpawu zokuphepha ezivamile emsebenzini, ukugeza izandla noma ezinye izinsiza ezivikelayo, ukuvikela abasebenzi ekubhekaneni ubumsebenzi, ukuvikela ubuso kanye nokugqwashwa kwe-ngqwashana noma ukufinyelela ezindini.
Abasebenzi abakuleli qembu elisengozini akuvamile ukuba badinge ukusebenzisa imishini yokuphefumula.
Uma umuntu egula endizeni, ukulawula okufanele ukuvikela abasebenzi nabanye abagibeli kuhlanganisa ukuhlukanisa umuntu ogulayo kwabanye abantu ibanga elingamamitha ayisithupha, ukubela ilungu elilodwa leqembu ukuba lisebenzele umuntu ogulayo, nokunikeza umuntu ogulayo imaski yobuso noma ukucela umuntu ogulayo ukuba amboze umlomo nekhala lakhe ngezindwangu lapho ekhwehlela noma ethimula.
Abasebenzi abasebenza emkhunjini kufanele bagqoke amagilavu ezokwelapha alahlwayo lapho benakekela umhambi ogulayo noma lapho bethinta uketshezi lomzimba noma izindawo ezingase zingcoliswe, futhi mhlawumbe bafake nemishini eyengeziwe yokuzivikela uma umhambi ogulayo enomkhuhlane, ekhwehlela njalo noma enenkinga yokuphefumula.
Amagilavu nezinye izinto ezilahlwayo kufanele zilahlwe esikhwameni sezinto eziyingozi, futhi izindawo ezingcolisiwe kufanele zihlanzwe futhi zihlatshwe amagciwane ngemva kwalokho. Ezokuthutha ezentengiselwano, kuhlanganise nemikhumbi yokuhamba ngezinyawo nezinye imikhumbi yabagibeli, ukulawula ingozi kuhlanganisa ukuhlehlisa uhambo uma ugula, nokuzihlukanisa nokuxwayisa ngokushesha isikhungo sezokwelapha esisemkhunjini uma umuntu eba nomkhuhlane noma ezinye izimpawu ngenkathi esemkhunjini.
Okuhle kakhulu, ukulandelwa kwezokwelapha kufanele kwenzeke ekamelweni lomuntu ohlukanisiwe. Ezikoleni nasezikhungweni zokunakekela izingane, i-CDC incoma ukuvalwa kwesikhashana ukuze kuhlanzwe noma kubulawe amagciwane uma umuntu onegciwane ebesesakhiweni sesikole kungakhathalekile ukuthi isakazeke kanjani emphakathini.
Lapho kunokusakazeka komphakathi okuncane kuya kokulinganiselwe, amasu okuhlukanisa abantu angasetshenziswa njengokukhansela uhambo, imihlangano, neminye imihlangano emikhulu efana nemfundo yomzimba noma amakilasi ekwaya noma ukudla endaweni yokudlela, ukwandisa isikhala phakathi kwedeski, ukunciphisa izikhathi zokufika nezokuxoshwa, ukunciphisa izivakashi ezingadingekile, nokusebenzisa indawo ehlukile yehhovisi lezempilo yezingane ezinezimpawu ezifana nomkhuhlane.
Lapho kunokudluliselwa okukhulu emphakathini wendawo, ngaphezu kwamasu okuhlukanisa abantu, kungacatshangelwa ukuxoshwa esikoleni isikhathi eside. Kwabasebenzi bezokuphoqelela umthetho abenza imisebenzi yansuku zonke, ingozi esheshayo yezempilo ibhekwa njengephansi yi-CDC.
Izikhulu zokuphoqelela umthetho okumele zixhumane nabantu abaqinisekisiwe noma abasolwa ukuthi bane-COVID-19 kunconywa ukuba balandele imihlahlandlela efanayo neyabasebenzi bezokwelapha abaphuthumayo, kuhlanganise nemishini efanele yokuzivikela.
Uma kwenzeka kuthintana eduze ngesikhathi kuboshwa, abasebenzi kufanele bahlanze futhi babulale amagciwane ebhande labo lomsebenzi kanye namagiya ngaphambi kokuwasebenzisa kabusha besebenzisa i-spray noma i-wipe yokuhlanza yasendlini, futhi balandele izinqubo ezijwayelekile zokusebenza zokuvalela nokulahla i-PPE esetshenzisiwe kanye nezokufaka nokuwasha izingubo.
I-OSHA ibheka izisebenzi ezithile zezempilo nezomzimba njengezisengozini enkulu noma enkulu kakhulu.
Imisebenzi enobungozi obukhulu ihlanganisa ukuhlinzekwa kwezempilo, ukusekelwa, amalebhu, kanye nabasebenzi bezokuthutha ezokwelapha abavezwa yiziguli ze-COVID-19 ezaziwayo noma ezisolwayo.
Lezi ziba sengozini enkulu kakhulu uma abasebenzi benza izinqubo zokukhiqiza ama-aerosol, noma beqoqa noma bephatha amasampula avela ezigulini ezaziwa noma ezisolwa nge-COVID-19.
Izinqubo zokukhiqiza ama-aerosol zihlanganisa ukufakwa kwamagciwane, izinqubo zokukhwehlela, ukubonwa kwamabhulukwe, ezinye izinqubo zokuhlolwa kwamazinyo nokuhlolwa, noma ukuqoqwa kwezibonelo ezihlaselayo.
Imisebenzi yomngcipheko omkhulu emathuneni ihlanganisa abasebenzi abahilelekile ekulungiseleleni izidumbu zabantu ababekwazi noma besola ukuthi banezimo ze-COVID-19 ngesikhathi beshona; laba baba sengozini enkulu kakhulu uma benza ukuhlolwa komzimba. Ukulawula okungeziwe kwezobunjiniyela kula maqembu asengozini kuhlanganisa amakamelo okuhlukaniswa kweziguli ezine-COVID-19 eyaziwayo noma esolwayo, kuhlanganise nalapho kwenziwa izinqubo zokukhiqiza i-aerosol.
Ukuphefumula okucindezela ngokweqile okukhethekile kungase kufaneleke kwezinye izindawo zokunakekelwa kwezempilo nezokufa.
Izibonelo kufanele ziphathwe ngezinyathelo zokuqapha zezinga le-3 le-Biosafety.
I-World Health Organization (WHO) incoma ukuthi iziguli ezizayo zihlukaniswe zibe izindawo ezihlukene zokulinda kuye ngokuthi zibhekene yini necala le-COVID-19. Ngaphezu kwezinye izinto zokuphepha, i-OSHA incoma ukuthi kusetshenziswe iziphefumulo kulabo abasebenza ngaphakathi kwamamitha ayisithupha ezigulini ezaziwa ukuthi zine-SARS-CoV-2, noma ezisolwa ukuthi zine-SARS-CoV-2, nalabo abenza izinqubo zokukhiqiza ama-aerosol.
E-United States, iziphefumulo ezihlungiwe ze-N95 ezivunyelwe yi-NIOSH noma ezingcono kumelwe zisetshenziswe esimweni sohlelo olubanzi, olubhaliwe lokuvikela ukuphefumula olubandakanya ukuhlolwa kokulingana, ukuqeqeshwa, nokuhlolwa kwezokwelapha.
Ezinye izinhlobo zezinsiza-kuphefumula zingavikela kangcono futhi zithuthukise induduzo yabasebenzi. I-WHO ayincomi ama-coversalls, njengoba i-COVID-19 isifo sokuphefumula kunokuba idluliselwe ngemithambo yomzimba.
I-WHO incoma kuphela ukuthi abasebenzi abahlola abantu abasendaweni yokungena bangagqoki imaski yokuhlinza.
Kulabo abaqoqa amasampula okuphefumula, abanakekele noma bathuthele iziguli ze-COVID-19 ngaphandle kwezinqubo zokukhiqiza ama-aerosol, i-WHO incoma ukuthi bafake imaski yokuhlinzwa, izibuko, noma isivikelo sobuso, ingubo, namagilavu.
Uma kwenziwa inqubo yokwakha i-aerosol, imaski yokuhlinza iyashintshwa ngomshini wokuphefumula we-N95 noma we-FFP2.
Njengoba ukuhlinzekwa kwe-PPE emhlabeni wonke kunganele, i-WHO incoma ukunciphisa isidingo se-PPE ngokusebenzisa i-telemedicine, izithiyo ezingokwenyama ezifana namafasitela acacile, kuvumela kuphela labo ababandakanyeka ekunakekelweni okuqondile ukuba bangene ekamelweni elinomguli we-COVID-19, basebenzise kuphela i-PPE edingekayo kulo msebenzi othile, baqhubeke nokusebenzisa umshini ofanayo wokuphefumula ngaphandle kokuwususa ngenkathi benakekela iziguli eziningi ezinesifo esifanayo, baqaphe futhi baxhumanise uchungechunge lokuhlinzekwa kwe-PPE, futhi bangakhuthazi ukusetshenziswa kwamamaski kubantu abangenazimpawu.
