INHLANGANO YENKULUNGWANE: [ICovid-19] Ukwehlisa umthwalo nokulungiselela ikusasa
ISIKHATHI/ISIKHATHI SOKUTHUMELA: 14 March, 2020, 00:24 UTC
Alikho ilungelo eligodliwe
Sithola ukuthi sizithola sisezimweni eziphawulekayo kule nyanga.
Ubhadane lwe-COVID-19 luyinto eyenza kucace ukuthi abantu emhlabeni wonke baxhumene futhi banemithwalo yemfanelo komunye nomunye.
Asinaso isandulela sezinselelo zalo, kodwa siyazi ukuthi impendulo yethu engcono incike ohlotsheni lokuzwelana, ukubambisana, nokwakha umphakathi emhlabeni wonke okuyisisekelo sale nhlangano.
Ubuhlobo nokukhathalela esikubone phakathi kwabo bonke esisebenza nabo nge-imeyili, izingcingo, nezingxoxo kuwukuhlola okuphawulekayo kwabantu abangakholeki esinelungelo lokusebenza nabo.
Ngingajabula kakhulu futhi ngiziqhenye kakhulu ngokubala nonke njengabalingani.
Ngesonto eledlule, othile wahlanganyela nami ukwazisa ngomsebenzi wethu.
Bangikhumbuza ukuthi kubaluleke kangakanani ukuba izwe likwazi ukuphendukela kuWikipedia manje, nokuthi kuyisibonakaliso esinamandla kangakanani salokhu kusetshenziswa okubucayi ukuba kuhlale ku-inthanethi futhi kutholakale kubo bonke.
Umsebenzi wakho wenza lokhu kwenzeke, kungakhathaliseki ukuthi ugcina amasayithi esebenza noma ukhokhela ozakwethu noma ugcina imiphakathi yethu iphephile.
Izwe lidinga ulwazi olunikezwa yi-Wikipedia, manje kunanini ngaphambili.
Lesi yisikhathi lapho kungeyona nje kuphela lokho esikwenzayo, kodwa nendlela esikwenza ngayo, okuzoba nomthelela omkhulu emhlabeni.
Ngenxa yokubaluleka kwalomsebenzi nendima yakho kuwo, sizobe senza izinguquko ezibalulekile endleleni esisebenza ngayo ndawonye, kusukela kuleli sonto elizayo.
Ukulungiswa komsebenzi wethu nezikhathi
Njengoba uRobyn asho ngaphambili, iqembu le-C lahlangana izolo ebusuku ukuze kuxoxwe ngendlela esizoyisebenzisa nesimiso sethu sezinsuku nezinyanga ezizayo.
Kule ngxoxo, sacabangela lokho esikucabanga ukuthi kungaba impendulo efanele kulokho esibhekene nakho nendlela engcono kakhulu yokugcina inhlangano iqinile phakathi nalesi sikhathi.
Ngokuyinhloko sasifuna ukususa ukucindezeleka futhi sisekele umsebenzi wethu isikhathi eside.
Uma udinga ukubuyela emuva, kulungile.
Kuwo wonke abasebenzi, izinkontileka kanye nabasebenzi besivumelwano:
okulindelwe ukuba sisebenze nsuku zonke kuyoba amahora angu-4 ngosuku, noma amahora angu-20 ngesonto kuze kube yilapho kunomyalo ohlukile.
Asimemezeli iholidi - uma ukwazi ukusebenza amahora amaningi, le nhlangano ingakusebenzisa.
Nokho, izwe alinakulindeleka njengamanje, futhi kungakhathaliseki ukuthi udinga ukunakekela abathandekayo, ukuthenga izinto zokuthenga noma ukuya kudokotela, inhlalakahle yakho iyona ebaluleke kakhulu kithi.
Asiqapheli isikhathi sakho.
Uma ugula, ungasebenzi.
Lokhu kufanele kube okuzwakalayo, kodwa siyakusho.
Awekho amalanga okugula noma ama-PTO adingekayo - vele utshele umphathi wakho futhi usize ithimba lakho ukuba libuyekeze amakhalenda nezikhathi zokuhlela ukuze uqiniseke ukuthi izindawo eziyinhloko zomsebenzi ziyasetshenziswa.
(Uma uthola ukuthi une-COVID-19, sicela wazise uBryan ngaphakathi kwe-T&amp;C Ops ukuze i-T&amp;C ikwazi ukusiza ngokusekela futhi iqinisekise ukuthi isimo sakho sithola ukunakwa okufanele kubaphathi).
Abantu abenza umsebenzi ngehora bayokhokhelwa ngokugcwele.
Sesivele sikushilo, futhi siyazibophezela ukuhlonipha izibopho zethu kosonkontileka bethu kanye nozakwethu abasebenza ngehora.
Wonke umuntu uyokhokhelwa ngokwezinga lamahora ajwayelekile asetshenziswe ngaphansi kwezimo ezivamile.
Lokhu kuhlanganisa uma ugula futhi ungakwazi ukusebenza.
Uma ufuna ukusebenza, siyakusekela.
Abantu abaningi basebenzisa umsebenzi njengendlela yokuxhumana nokucindezeleka kwabo nezwe elisizungezile.
Lokho esikwenzayo kungaba okuzuzisa kakhulu, ikakhulukazi ngezikhathi ezinjengalezi.
Nakulokhu, lokhu kumayelana nokuzinakekela kwakho.
Sicela ukuba uxhumane nomphathi wakho, ukuze sazi ukuthi yini okumelwe siyilindele futhi sikwazi ukuzivumelanisa nezimo.
Omunye umsebenzi ubhekwa njengobalulekile.
Kunezinto ezithile okumelwe siqhubeke sizenza.
Amaqembu e-SRE, HR Ops, Trust &amp; Safety, ne-Fundraising (phakathi kwabanye) enza umsebenzi obalulekile okungase kudingeke ukuba asekelwe okwengeziwe.
Sizoqala inqubo nayo yonke iminyango yokuhlola izinhloso zamanje bese sigxila ekusekeleni lokho okuyisidingo emizamweni yethu.
Kunokuningi okumelwe sikwenze sonke, kodwa sonke sizogxila kumaphrojekthi abaluleke kakhulu.
Ukwehlisa ijubane manje ngeke kulimaze kamuva.
Asihleleli ukuqhubeka "ngesikhathi esiphindwe kabili" ukuze sifinyelele umvuthwandaba uma usuqedile.
Ngeke ulindeleke ukuba usebenze amahora engeziwe ukuze uhlangabezane nemikhawulo yesikhathi manje engase ingafinyeleleki.
Siyavuma ukuthi izimo sezishintshile, futhi sizosebenzela ukubeka imigomo emisha nezikhathi lapho kufanele khona.
Kwenzekani nge-APP (Ukuhlela Kwonyaka)?
Ukuze sivumelane neqiniso lethu elisha kanye nokulindelwe kwamahora okusebenza nsuku zonke, sihlose ukulungisa umugqa wesikhathi wokuthumela uhlelo lwethu lwaminyaka yonke lwango-2020-2021.
Inhloso yethu ukuphakamisa ukunwetshwa kohlelo lwethu lwango-2019-2020 oluvumela isikhathi esithe xaxa sokwenza isabelomali ukuze kuvunyelwe abasebenzi ukuba babeke phambili umsebenzi obalulekile, ukuzinakekela, nokunakekela abathandekayo ngenkathi kuhlanganiswa nalabo abadinga noma abafisa ukusebenza isikhathi esincishisiwe emasontweni ambalwa ezayo.
Lokhu kwehliswa kwesikhathi kunciphisa kakhulu imithwalo yemisebenzi yokuhlela yamanje nengcindezi kuyo yonke inhlangano.
Sizokwethula isiphakamiso sethu eBhodi ngesonto elizayo futhi sizokwazisa izihambeli namaqembu ngezinyathelo ezilandelayo ngokushesha nje lapho sesithole ukuqinisekiswa.
Ngiyabonga eqenjini le-APP ngokuhola kwakho kulokhu.
Isimo sehhovisi, ukuchayeka nokuhlanzwa
Ngesonto eledlule, sathola ukuthi omunye wabalingani bethu base-SF kungenzeka ukuthi wavezwa igciwane le-COVID-19.
Nokho, ngenxa yokuqapha okukhulu, saqasha iqembu lokuhlanza elilwa namagciwane ukuze lihlanze zonke izindawo ehhovisi laseSan Francisco.
Basebenzisa isixazululo esibulalayo esibulalayo esivela esibhedlela ukuze babulale amagciwane kuwo wonke amafulethi, kanye nasendlini yokungenisa izihambi nasezinhlalweni zokugibela ezifinyelela esitezi sethu.
Lesi sakhiwo sisebenzisa umthetho waso wokunakekela izidingo zabanye besebenzisa imikhiqizo esekela ukuphepha kwabaqashi baso.
Sizizwa sikhululekile ukuthi ihhovisi liyobe lilungiselelwe kahle lapho sinquma ukubuyela.
Ihhovisi lethu laseDC lisendaweni ye-WeWork, eye yahlanganyela nathi kanye nawo wonke amalungu abasebenzi baseDC inqubo yayo ye-COVID-19.
Kusukela ngesonto eledlule, ihhovisi lethu laseD.C. liye lathuthela endaweni ekude ngokuphelele ngokuvumelana nesiqondiso esabiwe neSan Francisco.
Njengoba abanye kozakwethu baseNew York bazi, besilokhu sixoxa ngokuqasha indawo eBrooklyn.
Lezi zingxoxo ziyaqhubeka kodwa zingase zibambezele.
Abanye kozakwethu basebenza kude okokuqala ngqa.
Ozakwethu abasekude abahlala isikhathi eside bayazi ukuthi kungase kube ukuguqulwa, futhi bafuna ukukunikeza iseluleko:
Nciphisa ubude bemihlangano kuze kube isikhathi esingehora elilodwa noma amabili.
Uma kudingeka ukuba kube nezikhathi ezinde, cabanga ngendlela ongazihlukanisa ngayo phakathi nezinsuku eziningana.
Chaza ngokucacile umhlangano, ubeke uhlelo, futhi uthumele izinto zokufunda kusengaphambili.
Yenza ividiyo ibe yinto evamile, ngamathuluzi afana ne-Google Docs ne-Zoom ukuze kube lula ukusebenzisana nokuxhumana bukhoma.
Yiba nomuntu ozoqondisa yonke imihlangano, othile ozobuka ingxoxo ukuze athole imibuzo futhi alandelele uhlu lwezikhulumi, nomuntu ozokusiza ukuba abhale amanothi (noma abhale amanothi ngokubambisana).
Thumela i-imeyili kusekela lobuchwepheshe uma udinga i-headset ekhululekile.
Sebenzisa imali yakho yokubuyiselwa imali yokudla okulula.
Joyina isiteshi se- #remoties ku-Slack ukuze uxoxe nozakwenu ngomsebenzi ohlukanisiwe
Ithimba le-HR Operations libheka ukuqondiswa kwe-ergonomics okusekelwe kwi-webinar ukuze kusekelwe ukwanda komsebenzi ohlukanisiwe kulo lonke iSisekelo.
Kuleli sonto eledlule sicele bonke abathola izibonelelo zomphakathi ukuthi bakhansele imicimbi yomphakathi exhaswa yiWikimedia, efana nama-editathons, kuze kube yilapho i-WHO imemezela ukuthi ubhadane seluphelile.
Sabazisa ukuthi siyaqonda ukuthi isicelo sethu sokukhansela nezinye izinselele singenza kube nzima ukuqedela imisebenzi yabo yokuxhasa evunyelwene ngayo nokuthi akekho oyokwahlulelwa ngokuhlehlisa noma ngokushintsha lezo zinhloso.
Kuleli sonto elizayo sizoqhubeka nokunikeza iziqondiso ezengeziwe ngeWikimania nezinye izingqungquthela zomphakathi zesifunda nezomkhakha.
Imizwa evamile evela emphakathini womhlaba wonke ibonakala iyinjabulo ngenxa yokuphazanyiswa kodwa futhi iyaduduza ngenxa yokucaca nokukwazi ukugxila emiphakathini yabo, iWikimedia kanye nezinye.
Ngokuqhubekayo, i-CRT isebenza ukusetha ikhasi ku-Meta-Wiki ukuze inikeze indawo yomphakathi yokubheka umthelela futhi ilandele ukuxhumana kwethu nabo.
Ukuhlala uxhumene ngezindaba ezihlobene ne-COVID-19
Sizothumela isimemo kuma-calendar enu ngoLwesine oluzayo, ngo-14:00 UTC/07:00 PT somhlangano okhethekile wabasebenzi.
Sizosebenzisa lesi sikhathi ukwabelana ngolwazi olwengeziwe, ukuphendula imibuzo yakho nokuchitha isikhathi esithile sixhumana.
Sikhona ndawonye futhi silapha ukuze sisize noma ngabe singakwazi.
Okwamanje, ungaqhubeka nokuthola ulwazi olutholakala kule imeyili, kanye nalo lonke ulwazi olubalulekile oluhlobene ne-COVID-19, ku-Office Wiki.
I-CRT izogcina la makhasi eselokhu esekhona futhi igcine lonke ulwazi endaweni eyodwa.
Sisebenza futhi ukuze silondoloze ukuxhumana njalo nabasebenzi abahlala emazweni athinteke kakhulu njengamanje.
Uma unemibuzo mayelana nokuhamba, imicimbi, umsebenzi omkhulu, noma inselele yokutholakala, noma yini enye ongase udinge usizo ngayo, sicela ungangabazi ukwazisa futhi usebenze neCRT.
Silapha ukuze sinikeze ukusekela nokuxhumana lapho kudingeka.
Uma unendaba eyimfihlo noma ebucayi, sicela uthumele i-email kuBryan Judan - Umqondisi Wezokuxhumana Komphakathi Wamazwe Ngamazwe.
Akukho kulokhu kufanele kubhekwe njengokuyeka umsebenzi wethu nezibopho zethu.
Kunalokho, kuwukuqaphela ukuthi okwamanje, umsebenzi wethu nemithwalo yemfanelo cishe kuyodingeka ukuba sivumelane ngendlela ebesingenayo ngaphambili.
Lezi yizinyathelo esikholelwa ukuthi ziyadingeka ukuze sisekelane ukuze siqhubeke nokusebenza, sinikeze inhlangano yethu ukusekelwa abakudingayo, nezwe inkonzo abaxhomeke kuyo.
Umsebenzi wethu ohlosiwe uyobe usilindile lapho kufika isikhathi.
Okwamanje, sekuyisikhathi sokusekelana futhi sakhe indawo yomsebenzi obalulekile ozokwenzeka emasontweni noma mhlawumbe ezinyangeni ezizayo.
Siyanidinga nonke ukuze nifeze lokho, futhi ngakho-ke sidinga nonke ukuba nizinakekele nina nemindeni yenu ukuze nibe sesimweni esihle kakhulu lapho kuvela isidingo.
