b' I-angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) iyi- enzyme eboshelwe ebusweni bangaphandle (emembraneni amangqamuzana) amangqamuzana asemaphashini, emithanjeni, enhliziyweni, ezinso nasemagabeni.
I-ACE2 ilwisana nomsebenzi we-angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) ehambisanayo ngokunciphisa inani le-angiotensin-II nokwandisa i-Ang (((1-7) okwenza kube umuthi othembisayo wokwelapha izifo zenhliziyo. I-ACE2 iphinde isebenze njengendawo yokungena kumaseli amanye ama-coronavirus.
Inguqulo yomuntu yale enzyme ivame ukubizwa ngokuthi i- hACE2.
I-angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 iyi-metalloenzyme equkethe i-zinc etholakala ebusweni bamangqamuzana angaphakathi nangaphandle.
Iprotheni ye- ACE2 iqukethe i- N- terminal peptidase M2 domain ne- C- terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
I-ACE2 iyiprotheni ye-membrane yohlobo I edlula kanye, enendawo yayo esebenza nge-enzymatic ekhona emagumbini asezicubu nasemaphashini.
I-extracellular domain ye-ACE2 ihlukaniswa ne-transmembrane domain enye i-enzyme eyaziwa ngokuthi i-sheddase, futhi i-protein encibilikayo etholakala lapho ikhishwa egazini futhi ekugcineni ikhishwe emchameni.
I-ACE2 ikhona ezingxenyeni eziningi: I-ACE2 iboshelwe emngceleni wamangqamuzana amangqamuzana ase-alveolar, ikakhulukazi amangqamuzana esikhumba sohlobo II, ama-enterocyte esiswini esincane, amangqamuzana endothelial asezinhlangothini zemithambo yegazi nasezintweni zemithambo yegazi kanye namangqamuzana emisipha emincane yemithambo yegazi ezingxenyeni eziningi.
Ukubonakaliswa kwe-ACE2 mRNA kutholakala nasendle yengqondo, emathunjini, e-hypothalamus, nasezinhlayiyeni zobuchopho.
Umsebenzi oyinhloko we- ACE2 ukuba umelane ne- ACE.
I-ACE ihlukanisa i-angiotensin I hormone ibe i-angiotensin II eqinisa imithambo.
I-ACE2 yona ihlukanisa i-carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine ku-angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) bese iyidambisa ibe i-angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
I-ACE2 ingahlukanisa namanye ama-peptide amaningi kuhlanganise ne- [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, i-apelin, i-neurotensin, i-dynorphin A, ne-ghrelin.
I-ACE2 ilawula nokudluliselwa kwe-amino acid ethatha indawo engathathi hlangothi i-SLC6A19 futhi iye yahlotshaniswa nesifo sikaHartnup.
Njengeprotheni ye-transmembrane, i-ACE2 iyindawo eyinhloko yokungena kumaseli amanye ama-coronavirus, kuhlanganise ne-HCoV-NL63; i-SARS-CoV (igciwane elibangela i-SARS); ne-SARS-CoV-2 (igciwane elibangela i-COVID-19).
Ngokuqondile, ukubopha i-spike S1 protein ye-SARS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV2 ku-enzyme domain ye-ACE2 ebusweni bamaseli kuholela ekufakweni kwe-endocytosis kanye nokuguqulwa kwegciwane kanye ne-enzyme zibe ama-endosome atholakala ngaphakathi kwamaseli.
Le nqubo yokungena idinga ukuthi i-S protein iqale ukusebenza yi-host serine protease TMPRSS2, okuyi-inhibition yayo okwamanje ihlolwa njengendlela yokwelapha. Lokhu kuholele abanye ukuba bacabange ukuthi ukwehlisa amazinga e-ACE2 kumaseli, kungasiza ekulweni nokutheleleka.
Nokho, izinhlangano eziningi zezemisebenzi kanye nemibutho elawulayo iye yancoma ukuqhubeka nomuthi ovamile wokugwema i- ACE kanye nokwelashwa nge- ARB.
"Ukubuyekezwa okuhlelekile nokuhlaziywa kwe-meta okushicilelwe ngoJulayi 11, 2012, kuthole ukuthi ""ukusetshenziswa kwama-ACE inhibitors kuhlotshaniswa nokwehla okukhulu okungama-34% kwengozi ye-pneumonia uma kuqhathaniswa nokulawula. """
Ngaphezu kwalokho, "ingozi yokuqubuka komoya nayo yehliswa ezigulini eziphathwa ama-ACE inhibitors ezazinengozi enkulu yokuqubuka komoya, ikakhulukazi lezo ezazinesifo sohlangothi nokwehluleka kwenhliziyo".
"Ukusetshenziswa kwama-ACE inhibitor nakho kwahlotshaniswa nokwehla kokushona kwabantu okuhlobene ne-pneumonia, nakuba imiphumela yayingaqinile kangako kunengozi ephelele ye-pneumonia.
I- recombinant human ACE2 (rhACE2) kucatshangwa ukuthi iyindlela yokwelapha entsha yokulimala kwamaphaphu okubucayi, futhi kubonakala sengathi ithuthukisa i- hemodynamics yamaphaphu kanye ne- oxygen saturation ezingulubeni ezincane ezine- lipopolysaccharide- induced acute respiratory distress syndrome.
Isikhathi sokuphelelwa yisikhathi se- rhACE2 kubantu cishe singamahora angu-10 futhi ukuqala komphumela kuba imizuzu engu-30 ngaphezu kwesikhathi sokusebenza (isikhathi) esingamahora angu-24.
Imiphumela eminingi ibonisa ukuthi i-rhACE2 ingaba umuthi othembisayo kulabo abangabekezeleli ama-renin-angiotensin system inhibitors (ama-RAS inhibitors) noma ezifweni lapho i-angiotensin II ejikelezayo iphakeme. I-rhACE2 efakwe emithini iye yahlolwa ezivivinyweni zamakliniki ekwelapheni i-acute respiratory distress syndrome.
"Izinhlelo zokusebenza ze-b'COVID-19 ziyizinhlelo zokusebenza zesoftware ezenzelwe ukusiza ukulandelela oxhumana nabo ekuphenduleni ubhadane lwe-coronavirus lwango-2019/20, okungukuthi, inqubo yokuhlonza abantu ("abaxhumana nabo") okungenzeka ukuthi baxhumana nomuntu onegciwane".
