EChina, izinga lokufa lalingamaphesenti angu - 2,8 emadodeni futhi amaphesenti angu - 1,7 kwabesifazane.
Izizathu eziqondile zalokhu kwehluka ngokobulili aziwa, kodwa izici zofuzo nezokuziphatha zingaba isizathu.
Ukungafani kwemikhuba yokugoma okusekelwe ebulilini, ukwanda kokubhema okuncane kwabesifazane nabesilisa abahlakulela izifo ezihambisana nokubhema ezifana nomfutho wegazi ophakeme eminyakeni emincane kunabesifazane, kungase kube nomthelela ekufeni kwabesilisa.
EYurophu, ama-57% abantu abatheleleke kwakungamadoda kanti ama-72% alabo abafa nge-COVID-19 kwakungamadoda.
Kusukela ngo-Ephreli 2020, uhulumeni wase-US akabheki imininingwane ehlobene nobulili yokutheleleka nge-COVID-19.
Ucwaningo luye lwabonisa ukuthi izifo ezibangelwa amagciwane ezinjenge-Ebola, i-HIV, umkhuhlane ne-SARS zithinta amadoda nabesifazane ngendlela ehlukile.
Inani eliphakeme labasebenzi bezempilo, ikakhulukazi abahlengikazi, ngabesifazane, futhi banamathuba aphakeme okuvezwa yileli gciwane.
"Inhlangano Yezempilo Yomhlaba yamemezela ngomhlaka 11 kuFebhuwari 2020 ukuthi igama elisemthethweni lalesi sifo lizoba yi- "COVID-19".
Inhloko ye-WHO uTedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus wachaza ukuthi i-CO imele i-corona, i-VI imele igciwane, i-D imele isifo, kanti i-19 imele isikhathi lapho kwaqala khona ukuvela lesi sifo: ngoDisemba 31, 2019.
Leli gama lakhethwa ukuze kugwenywe ukubhekisela endaweni ethile (isib. iChina), izinhlobo zezilwane noma iqembu labantu, ngokuhambisana nezincomo zamazwe ngamazwe zokuqamba okuhloswe ngazo ukuvimbela ukucwaswa. Igciwane elibangela i-COVID-19 libizwa ngokuthi i-severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
"I-WHO isebenzisa "igciwane le-COVID-19" nelithi "igciwane elibangela i-COVID-19" ekuxhumaneni nomphakathi".
"Konke lesi sifo kanye negciwane kuvame ukubizwa ngokuthi "i-coronavirus".
"Ngesikhathi kuqubuka okokuqala eWuhan, eChina, leli gciwane nesifo ngokuvamile kwakuthiwa yi-"coronavirus" ne-"Wuhan coronavirus".
NgoJanuwari 2020, i-WHO yancoma i- 2019-nCov ne- 2019-nCoV acute respiratory disease njengamagama esikhashana aleli gciwane nesifo ngokuhambisana nesiqondiso sango-2015 sokungasebenzisi izindawo ezibizwa ngegciwane nesifo.
Amagama asemthethweni i-COVID-19 ne-SARS-CoV-2 akhishwa ngo-11 February 2020.
Ngenxa yokulinganiselwa kwamandla emikhakheni ejwayelekile yokuthengisela, abanye abakhiqizi be-digital banyathelisa izinto zokunakekelwa kwezempilo ezinjenge-nasal swab nezingxenye ze-ventilator.
Kwesinye isibonelo, lapho isibhedlela sase-Italy sidinga ngokushesha i-valve yokuphefumula, futhi umphakeli engakwazi ukuletha ngesikhathi esidingekayo, inkampani yasendaweni eyayisanda kuqalisa yasungula kabusha futhi yanyathelisa ama-valve angu-100 ayadingeka ngobusuku obubodwa.
Ngemva kokuqubuka kokuqala kwe-COVID-19, kwavela imibono yokuqamba uzungu, ukwaziswa okungamanga nokungaqondakali mayelana nemvelaphi, izinga, ukuvimbela, ukwelashwa nezinye izici zalesi sifo futhi kwasakazeka ngokushesha ku-inthanethi.
Kubonakala sengathi abantu bayakwazi ukudlulisela leli gciwane kwezinye izilwane.
Ucwaningo aluzange luthole ubufakazi bokuthi igciwane liphindaphindeka ezingulubeni, emandeni nasezinkukhu.
Awekho imithi noma umuthi wokugoma ovunyelwe ukwelapha lesi sifo.
Ucwaningo lwamazwe ngamazwe ngemithi yokugoma nemithi ye-COVID-19 luyaqhubeka ngezinhlangano zikahulumeni, amaqembu ezemfundo kanye nabacwaningi embonini.
"Ngo-March, i-World Health Organization yaqala i-"SOLIDARITY Trial"" ukuze ihlolisise imiphumela yokwelashwa kwemithi emine ekhona elwa namagciwane enesithembiso esikhulu sokusebenza kahle".
Awukho umuthi wokugoma okhona, kodwa izinhlangano ezihlukahlukene zenza imizamo yokuthuthukisa imithi yokugoma.
Umsebenzi wangaphambilini ku-SARS-CoV usetshenziswa ngoba i-SARS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV-2 zombili zisebenzisa i-ACE2 receptor ukungena kumaseli abantu.
Kunezindlela ezintathu zokugoma eziphenywayo.
Okokuqala, abacwaningi bahlose ukwakha umuthi wokugoma ogcwele.
Ukusetshenziswa kwegciwane elinjalo, kungakhathaliseki ukuthi alisebenzi noma lifile, kuhloswe ngalo ukuvusa ukusabela komzimba womuntu ngokushesha emagunjini omzimba lapho kutholakala igciwane elisha le-COVID-19.
Isu lesibili, i-subunit vaccines, lihlose ukudala umuthi wokugoma owenza isimiso somzimba sokuzivikela singakwazi ukubhekana ne-virus.
Endabeni ye-SARS-CoV-2, ucwaningo olunjalo lugxile ku-S-spike protein esiza leli gciwane ukuba lingenele i-ACE2 enzyme receptor.
Indlela yesithathu iwukugomela nge-nucleic acid (i-DNA noma i-RNA vaccine, indlela entsha yokugoma).
Imithi yokugoma yokuhlola kunoma yimaphi ala maqhinga kwakuzodingeka ihlolwe ukuze ibonakale ukuthi iphephile futhi iyasebenza yini. Ngo-16 Mashi 2020, kwaqala ukuhlolwa kokuqala komuthi wokugoma ngezisebenzi zokuzithandela ezine eSeattle.
Umuthi wokugoma uqukethe ikhodi yezakhi zofuzo engenangozi ekopishwe kusuka ku-virus ebangela lesi sifo. Ukuthuthukiswa okuxhomeke kumagciwane kuye kwasikiselwa njengenselele engase ibe khona ekuthuthukisweni komuthi wokugoma we-SARS-COV-2, kodwa lokhu kuyimpikiswano.
Kukhona ukuhlolwa kwemitholampilo okungaphezu kuka-300 okuqhubekayo kusukela ngo-April 2020.
Ukuhlolwa okuyisikhombisa kwakuhlolwa izindlela zokwelapha i-malaria esezivunyelwe kakade, kuhlanganise nezifundo ezine ezihilela i-hydroxychloroquine noma i-chloroquine.
Izidakamizwa ezilwa namagciwane ezisetshenziselwa ezinye izinto zenza ingxenye enkulu yocwaningo lwaseChina, kanti izivivinyo eziyisishiyagalolunye zesigaba III ze-remdesivir emazweni amaningana kufanele zibike ekupheleni kuka-Ephreli.
Ukubuyekezwa okusheshayo kokuthuthukiswa kwemithi yokugoma neyokwelapha ye-COVID-19 kwakukhona, kusukela ngo-Ephreli 2020. Imithi eminingi ekhona elwa namagciwane iyahlolwa ekwelapheni i-COVID-19, kuhlanganise ne-remdesivir, i-chloroquine ne-hydroxychloroquine, i-lopinavir/ritonavir ne-lopinavir/ritonavir ehlangene ne-interferon beta.
Kunobufakazi bokuqala bokusebenza kwe-remdesivir, kusukela ngoMashi 2020.
Kwabonakala ukuthuthuka kwezokwelapha ezigulini ezazithola i- remdesivir esetshenziswa ngendlela enesihawu.
Ukuhlolwa komtholampilo kwesigaba III kuqhutshwa e-US, eChina nase-Italy. I-Chloroquine, eyayisetshenziswa ngaphambili ekwelapheni umalaleveva, yahlolwa eChina ngoFebhuwari 2020, nemiphumela yokuqala.
Nokho, kunezidingo zokuhlolwa kocwaningo.
Iziphathimandla Zezempilo zaseKorea naseChina zincoma ukusetshenziswa kwe-chloroquine.
Nokho, iWuhan Institute of Virology, nakuba incoma umthamo wansuku zonke wegremu elilodwa, iphawula ukuthi kabili lowo mthamo uyingozi kakhulu futhi ungabulala.
Ngo-28 Mashi 2020, i-FDA yakhipha imvume yokusetshenziswa okuphuthumayo kwe-hydroxychloroquine ne-chloroquine ngokubona kodokotela abalapha abantu abane-COVID-19. Iziqondiso zesiShayina zesiphakamiso 7 nazo zifaka i-interferon, i-ribavirin noma i-umifenovir ezosetshenziswa ngokumelene ne-COVID-19.
Imininingwane yokuqala ibonisa ukuthi kudingeka imithamo emikhulu ye-ribavirin ukuze kuvinjelwe i-SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
I-Nitazoxanide iye yanconywa ukuba iqhubeke ihlolwa in vivo ngemva kokubonisa ukuvimbela ukuhlushwa okuncane kwe-SARS-CoV-2. Ucwaningo luye lwabonisa ukuthi ukuqala kokumiswa kwe-spike protein yi-transmembrane protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2) kubalulekile ekungeneni kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ngokusebenzisana ne-ACE2 receptor.
Ucwaningo lwe-chloroquine ne-hydroxychloroquine nge-azithromycin noma ngaphandle kwayo lunemikhawulo emikhulu eye yavimbela umphakathi wezokwelapha ukuba wamukele le mithi ngaphandle kocwaningo olwengeziwe. I-Oseltamivir ayivimbeli i-SARS-CoV-2 in vitro futhi ayinayo indima eyaziwayo ekwelapheni i-COVID-19.
Isiphepho se-cytokine singaba yinkimbinkimbi ezigabeni zakamuva ze-COVID-19 enzima.
Kunobufakazi bokuthi i-hydroxychloroquine ingaba nezimfanelo zokulwa ne-cytokine storm. I-Tocilizumab ifakiwe emiyalweni yokwelashwa yiKhomishane Yezempilo YaseChina ngemuva kokuthi kuqediwe isifundo esincane.
Ihlolwa esigabeni 2 ezingekho ezihlotsheni ezihleliwe ezingeni likazwelonke e-Italy ngemva kokubonisa imiphumela emihle kubantu abanesifo esibi.
Uma ihlanganiswa nokuhlolwa kwegazi kwe-serum ferritin ukuze kutholakale iziphepho ze-cytokine, ihloselwe ukuvimbela ukuthuthuka okunjalo, okucatshangwa ukuthi kuyimbangela yokufa kwabanye abantu abahlushwa yilesi sifo.
I-interleukin-6 receptor antagonist ivunyelwe yi-FDA ngokususelwa ezifundweni zecala ezibuyayo zokwelapha i-steroid refractory cytokine release syndrome ephakanyiswe imbangela ehlukile, ukwelashwa kwamangqamuzana e-CAR T ngo-2017.
Kuze kube manje, abukho ubufakazi obulawulwa ngengozi bokuthi i- tocilizumab iyindlela yokwelapha ephumelelayo i- CRS.
Ukudluliselwa kwama-antibody ahlanzekile futhi agxilile akhiqizwa amasosha omzimba alabo asebeke balulama ku-COVID-19 kubantu abawadingayo kuphenywa njengendlela yokugoma okungeyona eyezokugoma.
Leli qhinga lahlolwa nge-SARS kodwa alizange libe nemiphumela eqinisekile.
Ukungasebenzi kahle kwegciwane kuyindlela elindelekile yokusebenza lapho ukwelashwa ngama-antibody okungaphenduki kungenza ukuvikela ku-SARS-CoV-2 kube khona.
Nokho, kungenzeka kube neminye imishini, njengobuthi obungase bube khona emagumbini omzimba obuxhomeke kuma-antibody kanye/ noma i-phagocytosis.
Ezinye izinhlobo zokwelapha ngemithi elwa namagciwane, ngokwesibonelo, kusetshenziswa imithi elwa namagciwane eyenziwe nge-monoclonal, ziyasungulwa.
Ukukhiqizwa kwe-serum yokululama, okuyi-liquid portion yegazi leziguli eziphulukisiwe futhi equkethe ama-antibody akhethekile aleligciwane, kungakhuliswa ukuze kusatshalaliswe ngokushesha.
